NK016(ma)001:0: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje phur pa lha nag gi
NK016(ma)001:1: dkyil 'khor mngon rtogs 'grel nyi ma'i 'od zer ces
NK016(ma)001:2: pa bzhugs / bla ma dang lhag pa'i lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)001:3: mnyam nyid chos sku gsang ba'i sku //
NK016(ma)001:4: longs spyod rdzogs sku sprul pa'i sku //
NK016(ma)001:5: sku lnga'i bdag nyid bder gshegs nyid //
NK016(ma)001:6: dpal chen he ru ka la 'dud //
NK016(ma)001:7: phrin las chog bsgrigs phur pa'i don //
NK016(ma)001:8: khog dbub mdo tsam bri bar bya //
NK016(ma)001:9: de la bka' rgyud thams cad la //
NK016(ma)001:11: lung ni mdog cod bdun gyi 'chad //
NK016(ma)001:13: man ngag dgos don lnga yi 'chad //
NK016(ma)001:14: 'di ni lung la ma bsten pa'i //
NK016(ma)001:15: man ngag yin phyir dgos don lnga //
NK016(ma)001:16: slob dpon lo rgyus don dang ni //
NK016(ma)001:17: rtsa ba mtshan dang yo ga phyogs //
NK016(ma)001:18: gdams ngag dgos ched sa gcod tshig /
NK016(ma)001:19: dang po lo rgyus gleng bzhi ni //
NK016(ma)001:20: lha la grags dang mi la grags //
NK016(ma)001:21: mi dang mi min thun mong grags //
NK016(ma)001:22: rnam pa gsum du bshad pa las //
NK016(ma)001:23: dang po lha la grags pa ni //
NK016(ma)001:24: ston pa sgrol byed rgyal po des //
NK016(ma)001:25: 'og min bla med gnas mchog tu //
NK016(ma)001:26: rin chen dur khrod khang pa sprul //
NK016(ma)001:27: dbang phyug chen po'i longs spyod du //
NK016(ma)001:28: phyi dang nang dang gsang ba dang //
NK016(ma)001:29: kun bzang rol pa dpag tu med //
NK016(ma)001:30: bdag gis btab la mchod par byas //
NK016(ma)001:31: rdo rje khrag 'thung la sogs pa'i //
NK016(ma)001:32: khrag 'thung sum brgya drug cu dang //
NK016(ma)001:33: gtso bsgyur dkyil 'khor brgya rtsa brgyad //
NK016(ma)001:34: rdo rje ral gcig la sogs pa'i //
NK016(ma)001:35: gsang ba'i khro mo bye ba 'bum //
NK016(ma)001:36: sras mchog rdo rje la sogs pa'i //
NK016(ma)001:37: sgrol byed sras mchog stong rtsa brgyad //
NK016(ma)001:38: stag gis mgo can la sogs pa'i //
NK016(ma)001:39: sprul pa'i pho nya bye ba 'bum //
NK016(ma)001:40: dbang chen rol pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK016(ma)001:41: rang gi brtul zhugs drag po yis //
NK016(ma)001:43: mtshams rngam bskal pa'i me ltar 'bar //
NK016(ma)001:44: de tshe gdug pa kun kyang bsgral //
NK016(ma)001:45: kun kyang thar pa'i sa la bkod //
NK016(ma)001:46: gsang ba chen po mngon du shar //
NK016(ma)001:47: ya mtshan rmad du byung ba'i phyir //
NK016(ma)001:48: rdo rje gzhon nu'i thugs la brtan //
NK016(ma)001:49: sgrol byed bdag por dbang bskur te //
NK016(ma)001:50: ru tra la sogs gdug pa kun //
NK016(ma)001:51: sras mchog phur pa'i rtse la bsgral //
NK016(ma)001:53: rang rang 'dul skal ma lus pa //
NK016(ma)001:54: k+ai la ya'i rtse la bsgral //
NK016(ma)001:55: de tshe rdo rje gzhon nu yi //
NK016(ma)001:56: sgrol byed yag la 'di skad zhus //
NK016(ma)001:58: slad nas ma 'ongs dus ni ni //
NK016(ma)001:59: las dang skal ldan skyes bu yis //
NK016(ma)001:60: lnga rgya dus kyi tha ma la //
NK016(ma)001:61: gdul dka' sems can 'dul ba dang //
NK016(ma)001:62: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu tshar bcad phyir //
NK016(ma)001:63: drag po bsgral ba'i phrin las kyis //
NK016(ma)001:64: dkyil 'khor las dang bya ba rnams //
NK016(ma)001:65: ston pas bdag la gnang bar mdzod //
NK016(ma)001:66: de skad ces ni zhus pa dang //
NK016(ma)001:67: ston pa gsang mchog bdag po yis //
NK016(ma)001:68: drag po brtul zhugs phrin las kyis //
NK016(ma)001:69: bdag gzhan bsgrub pa'i thabs rnams ni //
NK016(ma)001:70: ljags kyis dbang por bkram nas bshad //
NK016(ma)001:71: rdo rje gzhon nu nyid kyis bsdus //
NK016(ma)001:72: rdo rje gzhon nu de nyid kyis //
NK016(ma)001:73: h'u mdzad phyag rdor gnyis la bshad //
NK016(ma)001:74: phyag rdor gyis bsdus lha gnas ni //
NK016(ma)001:75: gzhan 'phrul dbang byed lha rnams dang //
NK016(ma)001:76: ri rab rtse mo'i khang bzang du //
NK016(ma)001:77: brgya byin la sogs rnams la bshad //
NK016(ma)001:78: mi dang mi min brgyud tshul ni //
NK016(ma)001:79: drag shul yod pa'i rtse mo ru //
NK016(ma)001:80: gsang ba'i bdag po de nyid kyis //
NK016(ma)001:81: srin po blo gros thabs ldan dang //
NK016(ma)001:82: gnod sbyin rgyal po skar mda' dang //
NK016(ma)001:83: lha'i rgyal po tshangs pa dang //
NK016(ma)001:85: mi'i rgyal po nyid la bshad //
NK016(ma)001:86: blo gros thabs ldan yi ger btab //
NK016(ma)001:87: mi'i yul du grags tshul ni //
NK016(ma)001:88: gsang bdag le rgyal rnam gnyis kyis //
NK016(ma)001:89: dur khrod chen po'i brag phug tu //
NK016(ma)001:90: rgyal po yab sras gnyis la bshad //
NK016(ma)001:91: de la rgyal po yab sras kyi //
NK016(ma)001:92: gnod sbyin 'dus pa'i brag phug tu //
NK016(ma)001:93: bsgrubs pas rgyal ba mngon du byung //
NK016(ma)001:94: khams gsum dregs pa'i nyid du bsgral //
NK016(ma)001:95: gnod sbyin brag phug de nyid du //
NK016(ma)001:96: gnod sbyin rgyal po nyid la bshad //
NK016(ma)001:97: gnod sbyin rgyal po de nyid kyis //
NK016(ma)001:98: g.ya' ri gangs kyi brag phug tu //
NK016(ma)001:99: d+ha na sam kri ta la bshad //
NK016(ma)001:100: slob dpon d+ha na sam kri tas //
NK016(ma)001:101: bal po ming sring pho nyar btang //
NK016(ma)001:102: yang le shod kyi brag phug tu //
NK016(ma)001:103: pad+ma rgyal po nyid la bshad //
NK016(ma)001:104: slob dpon pad+ma rgyal po ni //
NK016(ma)001:105: pha med ma med rgya mtshor rdzus te skyes //
NK016(ma)001:106: rdzu 'phrul dbang gi pad+ma'i nang du 'khrungs //
NK016(ma)001:107: bsod nams dbang gis rgyal po'i bu skal byas //
NK016(ma)001:108: las kyi dbang gis bram ze'i phru gu bsad //
NK016(ma)001:109: rgyal po drin lan bsam pas ma bsad spyug /
NK016(ma)001:110: mda' lnga gzhu thogs nags kyi mdangs su song //
NK016(ma)001:111: pho byung bsad cing mo byung chung mar byas //
NK016(ma)001:112: yul mis ri dwags gshor ba bzhin du bdas //
NK016(ma)001:113: dpa' rtsal dbang gis rgyal bu stobs ldan bsad //
NK016(ma)001:114: rgyal khrims gnong bas za hor yul du ni //
NK016(ma)001:115: grogs gnyis mda' yis rtse mos ded de song //
NK016(ma)001:116: de tshe za hor slob dpon chen po ni //
NK016(ma)001:117: rgyal po pra b+ha hasti zhes bya la //
NK016(ma)001:118: gsum ka rab tu byung nas ming btags pa //
NK016(ma)001:119: sh+aakya bshes gnyen sh+aakya 'od du btags //
NK016(ma)001:120: slob dpon mtshan ni sh+aakya seng ger btags //
NK016(ma)001:121: rgyud kyi rgyal po de nyid 'dus pa mnyan //
NK016(ma)001:122: sras mo go ma nyid la dbang mnos nas //
NK016(ma)001:123: dkyil 'khor mthong dang dbang rnams rim bzhin thog /
NK016(ma)001:124: de tshe thos bsam tshol ba'i ched phyir ru //
NK016(ma)001:125: phur pa sde bdun ne r+aa dza rar mnyan //
NK016(ma)001:126: pad+ma dpal chen za hor yul du mnyan //
NK016(ma)001:127: spyi rgyud sde gsum mkhan po nyid la mnyan //
NK016(ma)001:128: 'jam dpal gshin rje bal po'i yul du mnyan //
NK016(ma)001:129: lta ba rdzogs chen rgya mtsho'i klong du mnyan //
NK016(ma)001:130: lung skor rnam drug rgya mtsho'i ngo la mnyan //
NK016(ma)001:131: de tshe thun mong mchog gis dngos grub rnams //
NK016(ma)001:132: rdo rje thod phreng rtsal gyis mngon du gyur //
NK016(ma)001:133: nus pa skyes nas rang yul rjes su dran //
NK016(ma)001:134: sngon du u rgyan yul du byon pa na //
NK016(ma)001:135: sngon gyi rgyus mkhan dag gis ngos bzung nas //
NK016(ma)001:136: rgyal po'i khrims kyi me dpung nang du bsreg /
NK016(ma)001:137: ma tshig sa gzhi thams cad mtsho ru gyur //
NK016(ma)001:138: mtsho la pad 'khrung pad+ma'i rdzing bu la //
NK016(ma)001:139: rdo rje slob dpon thod phreng bzhugs pa mthong //
NK016(ma)001:140: de la rgyal po chen po la sogs pa //
NK016(ma)001:141: yul mi mang po kun gyi ngo mtshar skyes //
NK016(ma)001:142: slob dpon mtshan ni pad+ma rgyal por btags //
NK016(ma)001:143: de nas yang le shod kyis brag phug tu //
NK016(ma)001:144: rdo rje phur pa'i rgyud rnams der bsdus nas //
NK016(ma)001:145: bka' dang gtan tshig thugs dam gtan la phab //
NK016(ma)001:146: 'jig rten dam can bcu gnyis dbang du bsdus //
NK016(ma)001:147: srog gis snying po gtan tshig ces pa ni //
NK016(ma)001:148: pad+ma'i rgyal po nyid kyis phyag tu phul //
NK016(ma)001:149: bswe mo bzhis ni rang gis skye rgyud bshad //
NK016(ma)001:150: shwa na bzhis ni mngag pa'i pho nya byas //
NK016(ma)001:151: re ti bzhis ni gsang ba'i mnyes pa phul //
NK016(ma)001:152: de tshe gdong dmar sku rgyal bod yul du //
NK016(ma)001:153: mnga' bdag khri srong lde'u btsan bka' btsan pas //
NK016(ma)001:154: gtsug lag khang bzhengs bod khams dregs pa khros //
NK016(ma)001:155: ci ltar bgyis kyang thugs dam ma tshar bas //
NK016(ma)001:156: u rgyan pad+ma yang le shod nas drang //
NK016(ma)001:157: rdzu 'phrul stobs kyis bod khams dregs pa rnams //
NK016(ma)001:158: ri rdo shod rdo lhag pa bzhin du bsdus //
NK016(ma)001:159: kun gyi srog gis snying po drang nas ni //
NK016(ma)001:160: ngan sngags sgrub pa thams cad de ru mdzad //
NK016(ma)001:161: de tshe btsad po chen po'i thugs dam yang //
NK016(ma)001:162: yid la bsam pa bzhin du 'grub par gyur //
NK016(ma)001:163: pad+ma rgyal pos rab tu gnas par bgyi //
NK016(ma)001:164: dkyil 'khor lha tshogs mang po mkha' la byon //
NK016(ma)001:165: dkyil 'khor lha tshogs pad+ma nyid la bskor //
NK016(ma)001:166: pad+ma nyid kyi dkyil 'khor lha la bskor //
NK016(ma)001:167: zhabs nas me byung sa gzhi kun kyang tshig /
NK016(ma)001:168: rdzu 'phrul stobs kyis lha 'dre mang po dang //
NK016(ma)001:169: lha brgyad klu brgyad gza' dang rgyu skar rnams //
NK016(ma)001:170: mngon du phyung ste kun kyang dam la btags //
NK016(ma)001:171: de tshe rgyal po chen po la sogs pa'i //
NK016(ma)001:172: rje 'bangs nyi shu rtsa lngar dbang bskur bgyis //
NK016(ma)001:173: kun gyi rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor mngon du mthong //
NK016(ma)001:174: ska ba dpal brtsegs skad bzhi lo ts+aa bgyis //
NK016(ma)001:175: rgya gar skad bzhi rangs pa bod du bsgyur //
NK016(ma)001:176: de tshe rdo rje bdud 'joms la sogs pa'i //
NK016(ma)001:177: skal ba ldan pa'i gang zag bdun po la //
NK016(ma)001:178: phur bu'i dbang bskur bka'i byin rlabs gnang //
NK016(ma)001:179: phur bu rgyud lung man ngag gsum po yang //
NK016(ma)001:180: rgyud dang man ngag gal po'i phyungs dang bcas //
NK016(ma)001:181: thams cad kun gyi gtan tshig man ngag rnams //
NK016(ma)001:182: rdo rje bdud 'jom dpal gyi seng ge dang //
NK016(ma)001:183: sh+aakya pra b+ha mkhon chen dbang phyug dang //
NK016(ma)001:184: jo mo nyid dang lnga la khyad par gnang //
NK016(ma)001:185: de'i nang nas khyad par gyur pa ni //
NK016(ma)001:186: bong chung don che tshigs nyung don mang zhing //
NK016(ma)001:187: bya sla thabs myur nyams kyi gdams ngag yin //
NK016(ma)001:188: phur pa rtsa ba rgyud kyi man ngag 'di //
NK016(ma)001:189: ban+d+he nga'i mkhar chen gza' la bshad //
NK016(ma)001:190: de nas dpal gyis mchod gnas stag gi rdo rje nas //
NK016(ma)001:191: klu'i rgyal mtshan byang chub shes rab dang //
NK016(ma)001:192: ye shes dbang phyug byang chub rdo rje dang //
NK016(ma)001:193: byang chub tshul khrims ga ljang dbang phyug dang //
NK016(ma)001:194: kye re grags pa sho mang can pa'i zhabs //
NK016(ma)001:195: rdo rje rgyal mtshan dam pa bde bar gshegs //
NK016(ma)001:196: 'gro mgon gtsang pa byams thos rnam gnyis dang //
NK016(ma)001:197: spyan snga zhang ston rnam gnyis ye shes 'bum //
NK016(ma)001:198: byang chub dbon po byang chub rdo rje dang //
NK016(ma)001:199: sang+ga gu ru badz+ra sh+r+ai dang ni //
NK016(ma)001:200: b+hud+d+ha b+ha dra bkra shis bla ma dang //
NK016(ma)001:201: dz+ny+aa na ke du g+ha g+ha bdag yan chad //
NK016(ma)001:202: brgyud tshul mdo tsam brjod kyis rgyas pa ni //
NK016(ma)001:203: lo rgyus chen mo rnams la gzigs par mdzod //
NK016(ma)001:204: rtsa ba mtshan gyi don bshad na //
NK016(ma)001:205: ngo bo dbyings dang ye shes la //
NK016(ma)001:206: nges tshig k+ai li k+ai la ya //
NK016(ma)001:207: ces pa'i sgra bsgyur phur pa de //
NK016(ma)001:208: phur ni lhun gyi grub pa'i dbyings //
NK016(ma)001:210: phur ni chos nyid skye ba med //
NK016(ma)001:211: pa ni rig pa 'gags pa med //
NK016(ma)001:212: phur ni kun gzhi gdal khyab yin //
NK016(ma)001:213: pa ni rang snang byang chub sems //
NK016(ma)001:214: phur ni gdal khyab chos kyi dbyings //
NK016(ma)001:215: pa ni 'gags med rol par shar //
NK016(ma)001:216: phur ni shes rab yum gyis mkha' //
NK016(ma)001:217: pa ni thabs mchog yab kyis dang //
NK016(ma)001:218: phur ni kun bzang yum gyis mkha' //
NK016(ma)001:219: pa ni bzang po rol pa'i rgyan //
NK016(ma)001:220: phur ni chos sku spros dang bral //
NK016(ma)001:221: pa ni gzugs sku kun la khyab //
NK016(ma)001:222: phur ni rang bzhin lhun grub la //
NK016(ma)001:223: pa ni phrin las rnam bzhi shar //
NK016(ma)001:224: de phyir phur pa zhes bya'o //
NK016(ma)001:225: yo ga phyogs kyi don bshad na //
NK016(ma)001:226: rnam pa gnyis su shes par bya //
NK016(ma)001:227: phyi dang de bzhin nang nyid do //
NK016(ma)001:228: nang yang de bzhin rnam pa gsum //
NK016(ma)001:229: rgyud dang lung dang man ngag go //
NK016(ma)001:230: phur pa 'di ni lung du gtogs //
NK016(ma)001:231: de la rnam pa gnyis su bshad //
NK016(ma)001:232: phur ba'i don gyi rnam grangs dang //
NK016(ma)001:233: rjod byed rgyud kyis rnam grangs so //
NK016(ma)001:234: don gyi rnam grangs gnyis yin te //
NK016(ma)001:235: mtshon bya don dang mtshon byed thabs //
NK016(ma)001:236: mtshon bya don la rnam gnyis te //
NK016(ma)001:237: lta ba dang ni ting 'dzin no //
NK016(ma)001:238: lta ba'i phur pa 'di lta ste //
NK016(ma)001:239: nam mkha' lta bu'i gang zag gis //
NK016(ma)001:240: rig pa ye shes phur pa de //
NK016(ma)001:241: gang khyab chos kyi dbyings su 'debs //
NK016(ma)001:242: rtogs ni snang srid lha ru gsal //
NK016(ma)001:243: 'bras bu gdal khyab chos kyi sku //
NK016(ma)001:244: de ni lta ba lhun grub po //
NK016(ma)001:246: nyi ma'i snying po lta bu yis //
NK016(ma)001:247: khyab pa thugs rje'i phur pa de //
NK016(ma)001:248: rang gi kun gzhi'i klong du 'debs //
NK016(ma)001:249: sangs rgyas sems can dbyer med mthong //
NK016(ma)001:250: 'bras bu sku lnga lhun gyis grub //
NK016(ma)001:251: lhag pa ting 'dzin phur pa de //
NK016(ma)001:252: ri bo lta bu'i gang zag gis //
NK016(ma)001:253: lhag pa sems kyi ting 'dzin ni //
NK016(ma)001:254: snang srid chos la gdab bar bya //
NK016(ma)001:255: rtogs ni snang srid lha ru gsal //
NK016(ma)001:257: chags ldan 'dod pa'i gang zag gis //
NK016(ma)001:258: chags can 'dod pa'i phur pa de //
NK016(ma)001:259: gsang ba yum gyi mkha' la gdab //
NK016(ma)001:260: bde stong ye shes rtag tu shar //
NK016(ma)001:261: 'bras bu zag bral bde ba thob //
NK016(ma)001:263: mtshon byed thabs kyis phur pa ni //
NK016(ma)001:264: tsan+dana sdong po lta ba yis //
NK016(ma)001:265: 'dod dang nga rgyal rngam sems can //
NK016(ma)001:266: gdul dka' 'dul bar dka' ba de //
NK016(ma)001:267: mngon spyod rdzas kyi phur pa de //
NK016(ma)001:268: byin rlabs ya mtshan ldan par bya //
NK016(ma)001:269: 'du shes gsum pa'i gzugs la gdab //
NK016(ma)001:270: gsal ba gsum dang ldan na thebs //
NK016(ma)001:271: 'bras bu bsgral bas tshogs gnyis rdzogs //
NK016(ma)001:272: rjod byed rgyud kyis rnam grangs ni //
NK016(ma)001:273: phur pa lung la rnam gsum ste //
NK016(ma)001:274: rgyud dang lung dang man ngag go //
NK016(ma)001:275: rgyud la yang ni rnam bzhi ste //
NK016(ma)001:276: rtsa ba 'byung ba'i rgyud dang ni //
NK016(ma)001:277: de bzhin bkol ba dum bu'i rgyud //
NK016(ma)001:278: mdor bsdus khyab pa'i rgyud dang ni //
NK016(ma)001:279: de bzhin phrin las shugs kyi rgyud //
NK016(ma)001:280: phur bu lung gis nges pa bzhi //
NK016(ma)001:281: rtsa ba dang ni bshad pa dang //
NK016(ma)001:282: bsgrub pa dang ni phyi ma'o //
NK016(ma)001:283: man ngag rtsa ba'i rgyud la yang //
NK016(ma)001:284: rnam pa drug tu shes bya ste //
NK016(ma)001:285: rtsa ba'i rgyud dang sgrub pa drug /
NK016(ma)001:286: khro bo bcu dang dbyings kyi yum //
NK016(ma)001:287: dam can dang ni bshad pa'i rgyud //
NK016(ma)001:289: rgyud kyi rnam grangs mdo smos tsam //
NK016(ma)001:290: bye brag rgya che gzhan du blta //
NK016(ma)001:291: 'dir ni bkol ba dum bu'i rgyud //
NK016(ma)001:292: de la brtan pa'i man ngag yin //
NK016(ma)001:293: gang zag dgos ched kyi don bshad na //
NK016(ma)001:294: phyi ma'i byang chub sgrubs pa la //
NK016(ma)001:295: bar chad dgra bgegs 'byung ba'i phyir //
NK016(ma)001:296: de dag bsgral zhing tshar bcad phyir //
NK016(ma)001:297: rdo rje phur pa 'di sgrubs dgos //
NK016(ma)001:298: sa gcod tshig gis don bshad na //
NK016(ma)001:299: klad dang gzhung dang zhabs gsum mo //
NK016(ma)001:300: gzhung don la yang rnam gsum ste //
NK016(ma)001:301: sku bsnyen gsung sgrub thugs phrin las //
NK016(ma)001:302: sku bsnyen la yang don bcu dang //
NK016(ma)001:303: gsung sgrub la yang don drug ste //
NK016(ma)001:304: thugs la dngos gdab rjes sbyang ngo //
NK016(ma)001:305: rgyas pa rang rang skabs bzhin no //
NK016(ma)001:306: slob dpon pad+ma'i rgyal po rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i skyes
NK016(ma)001:307: bus phur bu man ngag gis rtsa ba dan sngags
NK016(ma)001:308: tshig nyung la don che ba shin tu zab pa'i
NK016(ma)001:309: phur pa / skyi lugs gsang bsgrub chos rjes man ngag tu bkod pa 'di la gsum ste /
NK016(ma)001:311: shes bya'i chos kun ma lus lus pa med pa rnams /
NK016(ma)001:312: thugs dgongs pa la yongs su rdzogs shing /
NK016(ma)001:313: 'jig rten pa'i ma rig pa'i mun pa'i tshogs kun
NK016(ma)001:314: bcom pa'i ye shes sgron ma gsal bar mdzad pa'i
NK016(ma)001:315: bla ma bde bar gshegs pa'i zhabs la 'dud /
NK016(ma)001:316: sh+r+ai ni dpal ste de la gsum ni gzhi rang bzhin lhun gyi grub pa'i dpal /
NK016(ma)001:317: de nyid rig pa rang snang ba'i dpal //
NK016(ma)001:318: thugs rje chen po zhor las byung ba'i dpal dang gsum po ngo bo nyid kyis ldan zhing /
NK016(ma)001:320: bdag don la dgyes pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:321: gzhan don la dgyes pa rnam gnyis kyi sgo nas /
NK016(ma)001:322: du ra na chags pa ste /
NK016(ma)001:323: de la gnyis bdag don chos sku mi gtong nas chags pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:324: gzhan don 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa la chags cing /
NK016(ma)001:325: rdo rje ni de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi thugs ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid /
NK016(ma)001:326: gzhon nu ni thugs la bgres rgud med cing /
NK016(ma)001:327: gdul bya lugs ldog rnams kyi ngor khro bo chas
NK016(ma)001:328: kyis brgyan pa'i skur snang ba de la gnyis med
NK016(ma)001:329: mos / gzhung gis don la rnam pa gsum ste /
NK016(ma)001:332: thugs phrin las kyis dkyil 'khor ro //
NK016(ma)001:333: de la sku bsnyen pa'i dkyil 'khor la don bcu ste /
NK016(ma)001:334: dang po bden pa bdar zhing mtshams bcad pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:336: ting 'dzin rnam gsum sgom pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:338: brten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:339: ye shes kyis dkyil 'khor gzhugs pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:344: de la dang po bden pa bdar zhing mtshams bcad pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:345: gzhi chosa nyid kyisa bdena pa mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:346: de la gsang sngags kyis snying po brjod pas /
NK016(ma)001:347: gzhi skye med kyi chos nyid de rang gdangs 'gag
NK016(ma)001:348: med du shar ba'i byin rlabsa las lha'i skur shar
NK016(ma)001:349: bas so // yang na yig 'bru'i byin rlabs las lhar snang ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:350: der ma zad phyogs bcu dus gsum gyis sangsa rgyas thams cad kyis mthu yang 'byung ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:351: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba b+hig+hana bam h'u phata ces brjod pas /
NK016(ma)001:352: skad ciga gis ting nge 'dzina gyis /
NK016(ma)001:353: badga nyida bcom ldan 'adsa dapala rdo rje gzhona nur bskyed de /
NK016(ma)001:354: zhal gsum phyag drug sku mdoga mthing naga /
NK016(ma)001:358: phyag drug kasa phur pa dril te /
NK016(ma)001:359: dang po gnyis kyis sku'i phur pa dkar po dril ba /
NK016(ma)001:360: bar ma gnyis kyi gsung gisa phur pa damra po dril ba /
NK016(ma)001:361: phyag tha ma gnyis kyi thugsa kyi phur pa mthinga naga drila ba /
NK016(ma)001:362: rdo rje'i gshoga pa gdengsa pa /
NK016(ma)001:364: dur khrod chen po'i chasa brgyad dang ldan pa /
NK016(ma)001:365: mtshamsa rngam gzi byin dang bacasa pa /
NK016(ma)001:366: bskal pa'i me dpung gis nanga na 'gying bag gi
NK016(ma)001:367: tshul du bzhugs pa skad cig gis gsal bar bskyed
NK016(ma)001:368: do // phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad 'dus te bdag la thim par bsam mo //
NK016(ma)001:369: de nas bskul te rdo rje ni skye 'jig med
NK016(ma)001:370: pa sku gsung thugs rdo rje lta bu de rtogs
NK016(ma)001:371: dka' bas gasnga ba de nyid sangs rgyas kyis thugs
NK016(ma)001:372: la mnga' bas / sangs rgyas de'i bka' lasa ni /
NK016(ma)001:373: sdig can mi dge ba bcu la spyod cing bsgral
NK016(ma)001:374: ba'i zhing du gyur pa gang zhiga 'ad'a bar byed
NK016(ma)001:375: pa rnams / stobs bcu lhun gyis grub cing mi dge ba bcu tshar bcad nas /
NK016(ma)001:376: kro yog sde gsum las 'phags pas chen po khro
NK016(ma)001:377: bo chen po bcus glang pa ni mgo bo ste
NK016(ma)001:378: / nyon mongs pa'i rten shigs pa ste /
NK016(ma)001:379: tshal pa brgya ru khosa shig /
NK016(ma)001:380: de bas nyon ciga bgegas dang loga par 'dren pa'i tshogas /
NK016(ma)001:381: nga'i rdo rje gzhon nu bsgom pa'i bka' la 'da' bar ma byed cig /
NK016(ma)001:382: khro bo bcu'i sngags kyis rting par h'u ma ma
NK016(ma)001:383: pa sha ces tshang bar btags la brjod pa tsam
NK016(ma)001:384: gyis / thugsa ka nas khro bo mthing naga gcer bu phyag na phur pa bsnamsa pa /
NK016(ma)001:385: me dpung gisa nang na bzhugas pa bcu byung nasa /
NK016(ma)001:386: phyogsa bcura 'phros pasa phyogs bcu'i bgegas thams cad chung ba rnams che ba la bstim /
NK016(ma)001:387: de dag thams cad bgegsa kyis gtso bo phyogs skyongsa bcu la bstim nasa /
NK016(ma)001:388: khro bo bcus so sora bkug ste /
NK016(ma)001:391: mdun rgyab gnyis dang bcur bkug nasa /
NK016(ma)001:392: rdo rje khro dong nag po bcur bcug nas phyag gisa phur pasa btab te /
NK016(ma)001:393: 'og rdo rje'i brag ri la thal byung bar bsgom mo //
NK016(ma)001:394: phur pa'i dpal rtse la me 'abra ba dang phyogsa skyongsa bcu yang mera lam gyis 'abra ba dang /
NK016(ma)001:395: de ltar khro bo bcu'i sku la lhag pa ye shes kyis me 'abra ba dang /
NK016(ma)001:396: phyag gi phura pa la lhag pa ting nge 'dzina gyis me 'bar ba dang /
NK016(ma)001:397: phyogsa skyongsa rnams tshig pa la rnama rtog ye shesa
NK016(ma)001:398: su 'bar ba'i me dang gsum 'dres pa las me
NK016(ma)001:399: ri 'bar ba'i gur du gyur par bsgom /
NK016(ma)001:400: spyi don gnyis pa bshags pa bya ba ni /
NK016(ma)001:401: ye shes sku mchoga gzhung bzhin no //
NK016(ma)001:402: spyi don gsum pa ting nge 'dzin rnam gsum rim bzhin bsgom pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:403: rdo rje khros pasa zhe sdang gcoda /
NK016(ma)001:405: rdo rje ni rang nyid rdo rje gzhon nur gsal ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:406: khros pa ni thugs ka nas ram yam kham gsum spros pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:407: zhe sdang ni gzung yul ste /
NK016(ma)001:408: me chu rlung gsum gyi mi gnas par byed pa ni gcod ces bya'o //
NK016(ma)001:409: de yang dang po ram s+pha ra na phata /
NK016(ma)001:410: badga nyid rdo rje gzhona nu'i thugsa ka nasa ram damra po spros te /
NK016(ma)001:411: me byung basa 'jig rten gyi khamas thams cada ma
NK016(ma)001:412: lusa pa bsregsa nas me sbur bzhin du song bar
NK016(ma)001:413: bsam / sam ha ra na h'u /
NK016(ma)001:414: slar me'i lhag ma thugsa ka na tshur bsdu /
NK016(ma)001:415: yam s+pha ra ra na phata /
NK016(ma)001:416: thugsa ka nasa yam spros te rlung byung basa sngar
NK016(ma)001:417: bsregsa pa'i thal ba ma lus pa rasa bala rlung
NK016(ma)001:418: gis gtor ba ltar 'thora bar byas nas /
NK016(ma)001:420: slar rlung gisa lhag ma thugsa ka na tshur bsdu /
NK016(ma)001:422: yang thugsa ka nas kham spros te chu byung basa
NK016(ma)001:423: thal ba gtor ba'i lhag ma ma lus pa bkrus
NK016(ma)001:424: nasa / sam ha ra na h'u /
NK016(ma)001:425: slar chu'i lhag ma rnams badga gisa thugsa ka na tshur bsdu /
NK016(ma)001:426: de ltar gcod pa la ni mtshon chen ces bya'o //
NK016(ma)001:427: dper na 'jig rten gyi mtshon ral gri la sogs pas ni phyogs re bas mi chod pa la /
NK016(ma)001:428: 'dir me chu rlung gsum gyi snod bcud rags pa med par byas pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:430: sngon po ni cir yang mi 'gyur ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK016(ma)001:431: 'dir yang bsregs spyangs bkru ba rnam pa gsum gyis gzung yul dag par byas la /
NK016(ma)001:432: bar der 'dzin pa'i sems kyang ma grub ste /
NK016(ma)001:433: cir yang mi dmigs pa stong pa nyid du bsgom par bya'o //
NK016(ma)001:434: de yanga stong pa nyid kyi ting nge 'dzina ni /
NK016(ma)001:435: chos nyid cir yanga mi dmigas pa lasa /
NK016(ma)001:436: chos can cir yanga mi 'gyur ba ste /
NK016(ma)001:437: de bzhina nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin ces bya'o //
NK016(ma)001:438: 'bar ba ces pa kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK016(ma)001:439: stong pa nyid kyi nganga lasa de ltar ma rtogs
NK016(ma)001:440: pa'i semsa can rnams la snying rje'i nyamsa 'abra bya'o
NK016(ma)001:441: // nam mkha'i dkyil na thig pa shara /
NK016(ma)001:444: chos nyid nam mkha'a lta bu'i nganga yasa /
NK016(ma)001:445: ranga gisa rnam para shes pa'i ngo bo h'u /
NK016(ma)001:446: thugs chos nyid mi 'gyur ba mtshon pa'i mdog mthinga
NK016(ma)001:447: naga gcig gdang sol bcag pa'i mdog lta bu h'u
NK016(ma)001:448: cha lnga ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin yin pas 'ong
NK016(ma)001:449: kha dog lnga dang ldan pa thig pa ltar ranga
NK016(ma)001:451: gzhan du na de bzhin nyid stong pa /
NK016(ma)001:453: phyag rgya gcig pa dbyer med du 'dod la /
NK016(ma)001:454: yang na de bzhin nyid chos sku dang sbyar /
NK016(ma)001:455: sa ni kun tu 'od kyis sa /
NK016(ma)001:456: ye shes ni ji lta ba mkhyen pa'i ye shes so //
NK016(ma)001:457: kun tu snang ni longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku /
NK016(ma)001:458: ma chags par pad+ma can gyis /
NK016(ma)001:459: dbyer med lhun rdzogs kyi ye shes so //
NK016(ma)001:460: rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin ni sprul sku /
NK016(ma)001:461: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa /
NK016(ma)001:462: ye shes ni ji snyed mkhyen pa'i ye shes so //
NK016(ma)001:464: sa gsum sku gsum ting 'dzin ye shes gsum /
NK016(ma)001:466: spyi don bzhi ba rten gzhal yas khang bskyed pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:467: srog gis go ru shar ba dang /
NK016(ma)001:469: srog ni 'byung ba lnga yin te /
NK016(ma)001:470: 'dir yang de gnas su dag pa'i rtags su 'byung ba rim brtsegs bsgom pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:471: de yang h'u las e chad pa lasa chosa 'byung
NK016(ma)001:472: gru gsuma pa kha dog mthinga naga rgya khyon che
NK016(ma)001:474: 'byung ba nam mkha' gnas su dag pa yum kun tu bzang mo /
NK016(ma)001:475: ye shes ni chos dbyings ye shes so //
NK016(ma)001:476: h'u lasa yam chad pa lasa rlung gisa dkyil 'khora
NK016(ma)001:477: gazhu'i dbyibsa can rgya khyon che ba sra zhing mkhreg
NK016(ma)001:478: pa 'og rdo rje rgya gram gyis gtams pa srad
NK016(ma)001:479: med kyis bu'i mdas kyang mi phig pa /
NK016(ma)001:480: lag na rdo rje'i stobs kyis kyang mi shigs pa
NK016(ma)001:481: kha dog dud ka chos 'byung gisa dkyil du bsgom
NK016(ma)001:482: mo // 'byung ba rlung gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)001:484: ye shes ni bya ba grub pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:485: h'u lasa ra chad pa lasa me'i dkyil 'khor gru
NK016(ma)001:486: gsuma pa mdog sna lnga thug che ma 'ur sgra
NK016(ma)001:487: dang tshag tshag chem chem dang bcas pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:488: 'byung ba me rnam par dag pa na bza' dkar mo /
NK016(ma)001:489: ye shes ni so sor rtogs pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:490: ra chada pa lasa rak+ta khrag gisa rgya mtsho damra nag rba rlabsa 'khrugsa pa /
NK016(ma)001:493: chu rnam par dag pa yum m+aa ma k+ai /
NK016(ma)001:494: ye shes ni mnyam nyid ye shes so //
NK016(ma)001:495: lam chad pa lasa mam sa'i sa gzhi ste /
NK016(ma)001:496: sha chen gyis thang ma gadla ba /
NK016(ma)001:497: dbyibsa gru bzhi mdog ser bo'o //
NK016(ma)001:498: 'byung bas rnam par dag pa yum sangs rgyas spyan ma /
NK016(ma)001:499: ye shes ni me long lta bu /
NK016(ma)001:500: de ltar spyang bya 'byung ba lnga nyid /
NK016(ma)001:501: spyang byed ting nge 'dzin gyis 'byung bar ma brtsegs su bsgom ste /
NK016(ma)001:502: yum lnga'i rang bzhin ye shes lngar sbyar ba la /
NK016(ma)001:504: yang na phyi nang gis 'byung ba lnga nyid ye shes su shar ba'i phyir dang /
NK016(ma)001:505: phung po lnga'i 'khrul 'khor gcod pa'i phyir dang /
NK016(ma)001:506: dbyings phyug ma lnga lhun gyi grub pa'i phyir dang /
NK016(ma)001:507: 'byung ba lnga dang 'byung ba las gyur pa'i bgegs
NK016(ma)001:508: rig stong phrag brgyad cu dregs pa nga rgyal can
NK016(ma)001:509: rnams zil gyis gnon cing tshar bcad pa'i phyir /
NK016(ma)001:511: de'i steng du kem chad pa kenga rus kyis ri
NK016(ma)001:512: rab nag po kha khyer gyen du che ba khrag
NK016(ma)001:513: gi rol mtsho dang bcas pa'i ngos la bya sha
NK016(ma)001:514: zana mara po lding gisa zur la gacana khrag 'thung
NK016(ma)001:516: rak+ta khrag gisa zham chu 'abba pa dbyibsa gru bzhi pa /
NK016(ma)001:517: bang rim la ma bdun sring bzhi dang dbang phyug
NK016(ma)001:518: ma la sogs pa kun gyi gnas bca' zhing yod
NK016(ma)001:519: pa'o // zur bzhi'i mar la gnam lcags kyis mdzer chen bzhi dang ldan pa /
NK016(ma)001:520: zur bzhi'i yar la mkha' 'gro dbang du sdud pa'i dar chen bzhi phyar ba /
NK016(ma)001:521: de'i kha khyer la me mdog sna lnga dbyibs gru gsum /
NK016(ma)001:522: thugs chem 'ur sgra tshag tshag tu 'bar ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:523: yanga h'u lasa h'u ched pa lasa ri rab kyi
NK016(ma)001:524: kha lasa phoga te 'oda du zhu ba lasa rdo
NK016(ma)001:525: rje rgya gram rtse lnga para gyur pa phrin las
NK016(ma)001:526: bzhi mtshon pa'i rwa sha rwa dakara /
NK016(ma)001:530: lhun grub mtshon pa'i lte ba mthinga nag h'u gisa matshana pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:531: badz+ra ma h+aa rak+sha rak+sha h'u /
NK016(ma)001:534: rdo rje'i gur khanga du gyur pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:535: rkyen gyis mi tshugs pa'i rtags so //
NK016(ma)001:536: kha dog mthing nag rgya khyon che bar gyur pa /
NK016(ma)001:538: ri rab kyis steng yang rdo rje'i brag ri sra zhing 'khregs par gyur pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:539: chos nyid mi 'gyur ba dang ye shes chen po gsal ba'i rtags so //
NK016(ma)001:540: yang na rdo rje rwa bas bdud dpung 'joms /
NK016(ma)001:543: yanga h'u lasa b+h+r+aum mthing nag gcig chad pa de
NK016(ma)001:544: 'oda du zhu ba lasa dur khrod kyi gazhala yasa
NK016(ma)001:546: yon tan rgyas pa'i rtags su dbyibs gru bzhi pa las /
NK016(ma)001:547: rnam par thar pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i rtags su sgo bzhi pa sgo khyud can /
NK016(ma)001:548: phyi thod pa skam po lasa brtsigsa pa 'das pa'i sangs rgyas sam chos sku mtshon /
NK016(ma)001:549: bar thoda pa ra ri lasa brtsigsa pa da lta'i sangs rgyas sam sprul sku mtshon /
NK016(ma)001:550: nang thod pa rlon pa las brtsigsa pa ma 'ongs
NK016(ma)001:551: pa'i sangs rgyas sam longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku mtshan
NK016(ma)001:552: / yang na thod skam ra ri rlon pa gsum
NK016(ma)001:553: chos sku longs sku sprul sku gsum dang rim par
NK016(ma)001:557: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa dang gsum sbyar lugs yang snang /
NK016(ma)001:559: bar thams cad sha chen gyi brtsigs 'jim rak+tasa spyin thabs su sbyar ba /
NK016(ma)001:560: tshad med pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i rtags su /
NK016(ma)001:561: zur bzhir gnam lcags kyis 'dzer bzhi gdab pa /
NK016(ma)001:562: zur bzang po dpal gyis thod skam la 'od sna lnga yod par 'dod la /
NK016(ma)001:563: lo tsan+t+ra sing+hasa tri r+aa ga ni gsum rim ste /
NK016(ma)001:564: thod skam ri ri rlon pa sum brtsegs pa /
NK016(ma)001:565: de'i rgyab tu pany+tsa r+aa ga ni la rim ste /
NK016(ma)001:566: nang nas rim pa bzhin du sngo dkar ser dmar ljang rnams rin chen sna lngar 'dod la /
NK016(ma)001:567: de'i rgyab tu e ra ga rgyang rim la /
NK016(ma)001:568: me long lta bu'i ye shes kyis gdul bya'i rgyud la chos 'khor bskor ba'i rtags su /
NK016(ma)001:569: shar gyi rgyan 'khora los brgyan pa /
NK016(ma)001:570: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi gdul bya'i dgos 'dod skong ba'i rtags su lho rina po che /
NK016(ma)001:571: so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes kyis mtha' gnyis dbang du sdud kyang /
NK016(ma)001:572: mtha'i nyes skyon gyis ma gos pa'i rtags su nub pad+ma /
NK016(ma)001:573: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes kyis rang gzhan gyis
NK016(ma)001:574: don mthar phyin pa'i rtagsa su byang rala gris brgyan
NK016(ma)001:575: pa / chos dbyings ye shes kyi bar la dngos
NK016(ma)001:576: po thams cad 'jom zhing tshur la mi tshugs pa'i
NK016(ma)001:577: rtags su steng gru bzhi spyi bsdus te gur mgong
NK016(ma)001:578: snam pa'i rtse mo rdo rje rtse dgu pa'i bum
NK016(ma)001:579: pa / para 'khyil ba / steng thams cada rdo
NK016(ma)001:580: rje mthinga nag gisa pho gyo mo gyos brgyan pa
NK016(ma)001:581: pa / para 'khyil ba / / chos rjes de ltar du 'dod kyang /
NK016(ma)001:582: thos chog pas steng mtshon cha lngas bkab pa ye shes lnga /
NK016(ma)001:583: spyi bsdus rdo rje rtse dgu pa'i bum par 'dus pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:584: theg pa dgu rang byung gis ye shes su 'dus pa mtshon gsung /
NK016(ma)001:585: 'og gzhi e khram nyi shu rtsa gciga mthing nag ni /
NK016(ma)001:586: e gru gsum shes rab yum gyi mkha' dang gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin nam dbyings kyis rtags /
NK016(ma)001:587: byang chub sems kyi thig skal dkar po dang ldan pa ni thabs yab sam ye shes kyis rtags /
NK016(ma)001:589: thos chog pas e khram nyer gcig gru gsum khro dong du 'dod la /
NK016(ma)001:590: e nam mkha' ste dbyings dang /
NK016(ma)001:591: khram nyer gcig ni ye shes rnam pa cir yang sar ba'i rtags so //
NK016(ma)001:593: ye shes re re la'ang sku gsung thugs gsum gsum dang ldan pa'am /
NK016(ma)001:594: yang na drag po mngon spyod kyis gdul bya rgyud drag po rnams 'dul ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:595: dbus kyi gru gsum zla gam dmar po gsum ni
NK016(ma)001:596: khams gsum dug gsum lus ngag yid gsum dbang du
NK016(ma)001:598: mu khyud dkar la zlum pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:599: spros pa'i mtha' brgyad kyi mtshan mas ma gos pa'i rtags /
NK016(ma)001:600: mtha' gru bzhir gnas pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:601: lhag pa'i yon tan ye shes kyi rgyas pa'i rtags /
NK016(ma)001:602: lha snam damra po dang bacasa pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:603: ces pa ni 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das
NK016(ma)001:604: pa'i dregs pa can thams cad dbang du bsdu ba'i
NK016(ma)001:605: rtags so // thos chog pas bsnyen dus dang dbang la dmar po /
NK016(ma)001:606: bsgrub dus mthing nag tu 'dod do //
NK016(ma)001:607: pho brang rdo rje rwa ba'i nang du tshud pa ni chos nyid kyi khyab pa'i rtags so //
NK016(ma)001:608: gazhala yasa khanga gi rgyan yanga smon lam gyi shugsa dang ma bral ba'am /
NK016(ma)001:609: gdul bya'i bskul ba gasna pa'i rtagsa su bskal pa'i rlung nag 'tshub ba /
NK016(ma)001:610: rang byung ye shes kyis rtags su bsal ba'i me ri phyi nang meda para 'bar ba /
NK016(ma)001:611: sprul pa phyogsa bcur 'phro ba'i rtagsa su me re'i
NK016(ma)001:612: rtse la rdo rje rtse lnga pa'i snam pa'i thoga
NK016(ma)001:613: mda' 'phro ba / lo tsan+d+ra sing+hasa bzhed la /
NK016(ma)001:614: de rnams thod pa brtsigs pa'i kha na me 'bar ba /
NK016(ma)001:615: sna nas dud pa rlung nag 'tshub ma byung ba /
NK016(ma)001:617: rna ba nas zhag gis zo ris 'dzag par 'dod de /
NK016(ma)001:618: dngosa po thamsa cada semsa su rtogsa pa'i rtagsa su tsit+ta'i phol phying gisa brgyan pa /
NK016(ma)001:619: dug gsum gansa su daga pa'i rtagsa su /
NK016(ma)001:620: log rgyan sbrul nag gi za ra tshag gis brgyan
NK016(ma)001:621: pa ni rgyu skar gyi kha na sbrul gnyis gnyis
NK016(ma)001:622: bzung ba'i rngam gnyis kyi bar na zhing lag bzung
NK016(ma)001:623: ba'i d+r+wa 'phyang la ru sbal gyi mnga' yab btags
NK016(ma)001:624: pa dang / sbrul mgo gnyis kyi bar na tsit+ta'i
NK016(ma)001:625: phol phying te snying bzung ba'i d+r+wa ba ste za
NK016(ma)001:627: chos thams cad ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'i rtags su /
NK016(ma)001:628: mnga' yab mi'i lag pa dang rkang pa chab nas
NK016(ma)001:629: mchog yar la bslang ba pu shu de la 'khrungs
NK016(ma)001:631: rkang mthil lag mthil gyen du phyung ba'i sab srog sbrul nag las byas pa'i bcing thag ni /
NK016(ma)001:632: mi'i rgyu ma tshil chen gyi g.yos pas bcing ba'i
NK016(ma)001:633: rtsa ba'i bad chags su mnan pa la da ru
NK016(ma)001:634: kad kyis mda' yab du 'dod do //
NK016(ma)001:635: de'i nang du bdud rnams 'jom pa'i rtags su zhing tring /
NK016(ma)001:636: lha chen brgyad kyis rgyal mtshan ni /
NK016(ma)001:637: dpal chen po'i mda' yab du 'dod do //
NK016(ma)001:638: chos thamsa cad badga meda para rtogsa pa'i rtagsa su
NK016(ma)001:639: mda' yab gyis nang du rta bab kyis g.yas g.yon
NK016(ma)001:640: gyi thad du zhing chen gis 'aphana zar tshag gnyis
NK016(ma)001:642: mi mgo'i rtog 'od kha dog sna tshogs pa'i steng du mi snying gis brgyan pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:643: zhing lpags gis bla re ni nang gi gtso bo'i dbu thog na yod pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:644: zhi gansa dang lhag mthonga zung du 'brel ba'i rtagsa su /
NK016(ma)001:645: nyi zla'i skar khunga yoda pa /
NK016(ma)001:646: thugsa rje chagsa pa dang ma bral ba'i rtagsa su rak+ta'i zham chu 'abba pa /
NK016(ma)001:647: phyogs phyogs kyi sa rgyal po chen po bzhi 'dul
NK016(ma)001:648: ba'i rtags la sgo'i ru bzhi'i skyes bu byas pa
NK016(ma)001:649: / chos nyid 'gyur ba med pa'i rtags su /
NK016(ma)001:650: gnam lcagsa kyi ya thema yod pa /
NK016(ma)001:651: ma thim khro chu las byas pa /
NK016(ma)001:652: sbrul brgyad kyis sgo leb byas pas /
NK016(ma)001:653: chu srin la sogs pas sgo srog bsgrig pa /
NK016(ma)001:654: sgo thog na bcu gcig rdo rje'i re'u mig dang /
NK016(ma)001:655: sgo khang nang gis rgyan dgu dang bcas pa yod pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:656: yang sgo la zhing lpags dang /
NK016(ma)001:657: sgo 'dan sbrul nag la byas par 'dod pa yang snang ngo //
NK016(ma)001:658: rnam par thar pa brgyad dang ldan pa'i rtags chu
NK016(ma)001:659: srin gyi rta zur byas pa'i rta bab bang rim
NK016(ma)001:660: bzhi pa snam bu brgyad dang ldan pa /
NK016(ma)001:661: rus chen gyis pha gu la mu tig gis d+r+wa ba 'phyang ba /
NK016(ma)001:662: pad+ma 'dab ma stong ldan gyis bkab pa'i steng du /
NK016(ma)001:663: chos 'khor bcu gsum gang gis gdugs kyis brgyan pa /
NK016(ma)001:664: chos 'khor gyis g.yas g.yon gnyis su /
NK016(ma)001:665: 'brug gisa ri dwagas tshul du yod pa'i sgra sgrogsa pa ni theg pa mchog gis chos sam /
NK016(ma)001:666: mngon spyod kyis gzhan dbang du mdzad pa'i rtags so //
NK016(ma)001:667: yang na rta bab keng rus las byas pa'i bang rim bzhir 'dod pa yang snang ngo //
NK016(ma)001:668: bsnyen gnas brgyad mtshon pa'i rtags su /
NK016(ma)001:669: sa bdag gis ka gdan ni ru sbal ser po
NK016(ma)001:670: brgyad sgo g.yas g.yon gyis thad so'i lha snam dang
NK016(ma)001:671: / gru chad kyi mtshams na kha phyir bstan des yod pa /
NK016(ma)001:672: 'phags lam brgyad mtshon pa'i lha chena po brgyad kyis ka ba ni /
NK016(ma)001:673: zhing smug po brgyad lang pa'i lus la sbrul nag
NK016(ma)001:674: bzhi'i dkris nas bam tshang zar tshag tu yod pa'i
NK016(ma)001:675: mgo gnyis dang / rnga ma gnyis snyan gang na phyar zhing /
NK016(ma)001:676: mgo gnyis rnga ma gnyis pus mo mgo la phyar
NK016(ma)001:677: ba'i lag pa mgo thog na brkyangs nas dpal ka'i
NK016(ma)001:678: tshul du yod pa'i nang du nyi zla'i ka gzhu'i
NK016(ma)001:679: steng du rnam thar brgyad mtshon pa'i rtags su klu
NK016(ma)001:680: chen po brgyad kyis gdung ma byas pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:681: mgo phyogs bzhir bstan nas 'jug ma dbus su bsnol ba /
NK016(ma)001:682: chos rjes de ltar bzhed kyang /
NK016(ma)001:684: ka ba phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad du btsugs pa'i steng
NK016(ma)001:685: klu brgyad kyis gdung ma mgo phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad
NK016(ma)001:686: du bstan te / rgya gram du bres par 'dod do //
NK016(ma)001:687: brtsigs pa'i kha khyer gyis nang du 'dod yon ma spangs rgyan du rol pa'i rtags su /
NK016(ma)001:688: 'dod snam dmar po yod pa'i thog tu mchod pa'i lha mo gnas pa /
NK016(ma)001:689: bsgom dbang du nam mkha' bar snang sa gzhi gang bar bsgom mo //
NK016(ma)001:690: kha khyer gyis phyi ma la thod tshal gyi pha gu yod pa /
NK016(ma)001:691: nang du phyogs skyong bcu 'dul ba'i rtags su /
NK016(ma)001:692: zhing chung bcu'i ka thung gis bar du rus chen
NK016(ma)001:693: gyis trag rtse ste mi'i rtsibs ma bslab pa'i thog
NK016(ma)001:694: na / gza' dang rgyu skar gyis kha bad byas pa'i /
NK016(ma)001:696: mgo mtshams bzhir bsnol zhing mjug ma logs su bsnol ba'i kha bad kyis steng du /
NK016(ma)001:698: stong nyid bco brgyad 'dzoms pa'i rtags su rgyu skar nyer brgyad /
NK016(ma)001:699: nang gis gdung ma'i phyogs re re nas bzhi bzhi
NK016(ma)001:700: mtshams re re nas gsum gsum len pa'i dral grab
NK016(ma)001:703: de'i thog na sha chen gyis thog 'jim gyi steng rdo rje'i pho gyo mo gyo sbyi bsdus te /
NK016(ma)001:704: rdo rje nag po rtse dgu pa'i bum par 'khyil ba /
NK016(ma)001:706: chos rjes mtshon cha lnga'i steng kheb mi bzhed /
NK016(ma)001:708: las bzhis gzhan don mdzad pa'i rtags su /
NK016(ma)001:709: shar gyis sgo ske phyi gcad dakara /
NK016(ma)001:713: gzhal yas khang gis zur bzhi na /
NK016(ma)001:718: shang shang dang bzhi gnas par bzhed do //
NK016(ma)001:719: de'i phyi rol na ta la'i shing dang /
NK016(ma)001:720: gser gyis tshang tshang gis bres pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:721: theg pa thams cad kyis dam tshig rnam par dag pa'i rtags so //
NK016(ma)001:722: de'i rgyab rdo rje rwa ba'i nang du dur khrod sa gzhi dmar nag gis steng du /
NK016(ma)001:725: lce spyang stag gzig dom dred ro gsar rnying gis
NK016(ma)001:726: tshogs dang bcas pa'i nang na dbang phyug ma nyer
NK016(ma)001:727: brgyad la sogs ma mo thams cad kyis h'u h'u
NK016(ma)001:728: dang phata phata / b+h+yo b+h+yo ru lu'i sgra sgrogs par bskyed do gsungs /
NK016(ma)001:729: de'i nang gis gadna yanga gdul bya rtags la rgyal ba'i rtags su /
NK016(ma)001:730: dregs pa pho mo'i gdan ni /
NK016(ma)001:731: dbus su ru tra pho mo dang ma h+aa de wa pho mo bsnol ba'i zhabs na /
NK016(ma)001:732: pad+ma dang zla ba nyi ma brtsegsa pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:733: pho'i mgo gayasa su kha sbub mo gana rgyal mgo g.yona no //
NK016(ma)001:735: e khram nyi shu la khro bo bcu'i gadna nyi ma bcu'i steng du /
NK016(ma)001:736: phyogsa skyongsa gisa ro bsnol ma bcu bsgom mo //
NK016(ma)001:737: khra thabas kyis gansa su ro rkyang pa bcu /
NK016(ma)001:738: dam can gyis gansa su ro mgo med pa bcu gnyis bsgom pa chos rjes bzhed la /
NK016(ma)001:739: thos chog pas gtso bo'i gdan la gru gsum gyi
NK016(ma)001:740: nang du ru tra pho mo dang ma h+aa de
NK016(ma)001:741: ba pho mo'i steng du nyi zla pad+ma gsum brtsegs
NK016(ma)001:742: khro bo bcu la phyogs skyongs pho mo'i ro e
NK016(ma)001:743: khram gyis gru gsum gyis nang du bcug pa'i steng
NK016(ma)001:744: du nyi ma / khra thabs kyi gnas su ro rkyang pa bcu ni bsgral ba'i zhing bcu ste /
NK016(ma)001:745: ro glo nyal mgo g.yas su bstan pa'i steng du
NK016(ma)001:746: nyi ma lha snam la ro mgo med bcu gnyis
NK016(ma)001:747: zer yang / shwa na bzhi dang /
NK016(ma)001:748: re ti bzhi'i gdan ni lha srin sde brgyad yin
NK016(ma)001:749: pas mgo yod ces gsung bswe mo bzhi'i gdan ni
NK016(ma)001:750: bdud bzhi yin pas mgo med do //
NK016(ma)001:751: spyi don lnga pa brten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor gyis lha bskyed pa la bzhi ste /
NK016(ma)001:753: phyogs bcu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK016(ma)001:754: phur pa sras kyis dkyil 'khor dang /
NK016(ma)001:755: dam can srung ma'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK016(ma)001:756: de la bdag rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK016(ma)001:757: nam mkha'i h'u de dabus kyis gadna thoga tu baba pa lasa /
NK016(ma)001:760: 'oda du zhu ste rdo rje nag po rtse dagu
NK016(ma)001:761: pa khro nal bcu drug dang ldan pa me 'bar
NK016(ma)001:762: ba'i lte ba h'u gisa matshana pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:763: sangs rgyas kyis thabs ye shes dang /
NK016(ma)001:764: sems can gyis rnam par shes pa rnal 'byor pa'i
NK016(ma)001:765: ting nge 'dzin ngo bor bsgom pa yin pa de
NK016(ma)001:766: yang rdo rje rtse dgur gnas pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:767: sems can gyis dus su rnam par shes pa tshogs
NK016(ma)001:768: dgu de sangs rgyas kyis ye shes dgur gnas su
NK016(ma)001:769: dag cing / rnal 'byor ba'i ting nge 'dzin gyi ye shes dgur snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK016(ma)001:770: de la 'oda zera 'aphros pasa phyogsa bcu'i sangsa rgyas thamsa cada kyis sku gsung thugsa kyis rgyud bskul /
NK016(ma)001:771: semsa can gyis lusa ngaga yida gsum gyis sgrib pa sbyangsa /
NK016(ma)001:772: slar 'dus nas sngags brjod pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:774: +amo yi ge cha lnga ye shes lnga mtshon byed dam sa bon /
NK016(ma)001:776: na ro mnyam nyid ye shes /
NK016(ma)001:777: zla tshes me long ye shes /
NK016(ma)001:778: thig le so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes /
NK016(ma)001:779: 'a bya ba nan tan gyis ye shes /
NK016(ma)001:781: badz+ra rdo rje k+ai li phur bu k+ai la ya phur pa 'debs pa /
NK016(ma)001:782: sarba thams cad b+hig bgegs nan phur bu ri rab kyis mnan pa /
NK016(ma)001:784: h'u yi ge cha lnga sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lngar bskyed cig pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:785: phata ces spros pa zhes bya ba'i tha tshig go //
NK016(ma)001:787: +amo ni sku lnga ye shes lnga ste /
NK016(ma)001:789: na ro sor rtogs ye shes /
NK016(ma)001:790: zla tshes mnyam nyid ye shes /
NK016(ma)001:791: thig le me long lta bu'i ye shes /
NK016(ma)001:792: 'a bya ba grub pa'i ye shes so //
NK016(ma)001:793: de yang bkra shis pa'i don /
NK016(ma)001:794: sngags thams cad byin gyi brlabs par bya ba'i sngon du 'gro ba yin /
NK016(ma)001:797: stong pa shes rab kyis don yum gyis so //
NK016(ma)001:798: k+ai li ni sbra rang thad du phur pa la bstod de bos pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:799: lha ni khro bo yab yum bcu'o //
NK016(ma)001:800: k+ai la ni phur pas thob cig pa ste /
NK016(ma)001:801: lha ni za byed yab yum bcu'o //
NK016(ma)001:802: ya zhes sras mchog nyer gcig gis rang bzhin /
NK016(ma)001:807: h'u ni khams gsum rdo rje khro bo srin po'i lha tshogs /
NK016(ma)001:809: don la bgegs thams cad zung cig /
NK016(ma)001:812: rdo rje srin po'i lha tshogs kyis phur pa snying khar thob la sod cig pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:813: h'u rgyu ma nor brtsa ba'i sngags /
NK016(ma)001:814: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags /
NK016(ma)001:815: sarba b+hig+hana la sogs dad sbrel ba ni bzlas pa las sngags yin gsung /
NK016(ma)001:818: badz+ra rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum /
NK016(ma)001:826: nan bdag nyid chen mo bzhi /
NK016(ma)001:830: de ltar 'dod pa yang snang ngo //
NK016(ma)001:832: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata ces brjod pas /
NK016(ma)001:833: rdo rje gzhona nu'i skur gyur te /
NK016(ma)001:834: snying gi go ru bsgom para bya /
NK016(ma)001:836: rdo rje h'u dang bcas pa bsgom pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:837: snying rje'i bsgral ba'i dam tshiga ni /
NK016(ma)001:839: 'jig rten pa bzhin zhe sdang gis bsad cing /
NK016(ma)001:840: gti mug gis mnan pa ma yin te /
NK016(ma)001:841: 'od 'phros pas sems can gyis lus ngag yid gsum gyi sgrib pa sbyangs nasa kyang /
NK016(ma)001:842: rdo rje gzhon nu'i sku grangs meda para gyur pa la ni /
NK016(ma)001:843: phung po rdo rje gtam byas nas /
NK016(ma)001:845: de dag tshur 'dus te rdo rje gzhon nu'i skur gyur pa la ni /
NK016(ma)001:846: rnam para shesa pa rdo rjera bsgom /
NK016(ma)001:849: snying ni thugs yang dag pa'i ye shes /
NK016(ma)001:850: go ru ni de'i rtags rdo rje bsgom pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:851: de'i 'od zer 'phro 'du las 'gro ba'i don byas pa ni snying rjes bsgral bas /
NK016(ma)001:852: sgrol byed rdo rje gzhon nur bsgom pa /
NK016(ma)001:853: dam tshig ni yum 'khor lo rgyas 'debs ma bsgom pa /
NK016(ma)001:854: de ltar yab yum gnyis su med pas 'gro ba sgrol ba yang /
NK016(ma)001:855: zhe sdang gis bsad cing gti mug gis mnan pa lta bu ni ma yin /
NK016(ma)001:856: thugs ye shes kyis 'od 'phros sems can gyis lnga phung sbyangs te bsregs /
NK016(ma)001:857: slar 'dus bdag nyid rdo rje gzhon nur gsal ba'i
NK016(ma)001:858: ba sbu thams cad rdo rje gzhon nu'i sku tshon
NK016(ma)001:859: gang bas gtam pa ste reg ma reg tsam du
NK016(ma)001:860: gnas pa / gsung gi k+ai la ya sgrogs pa /
NK016(ma)001:861: sku la ye shes kyis 'od 'phro ba /
NK016(ma)001:862: sku bskal ba'i me dpung gis nang na bzhugs pa /
NK016(ma)001:863: gdul bya sems can yang de ltar gyur par bsgom pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:864: rnam par shes pa rdo rjer bsgom ces bya'o //
NK016(ma)001:865: de yang dabla ni phun sum tshogs pa /
NK016(ma)001:866: rdo rje ni rang byung ye shes skye 'jig med
NK016(ma)001:867: pa gzhona nu ni chos sku la bsgres gud mi
NK016(ma)001:868: mnga' ba / sku mdog mthing nag ni chos nyid 'gyur ba med pa /
NK016(ma)001:869: de yang dbu gsum rnam thar gsum mam sku gsum
NK016(ma)001:870: gyi ngo bo phyag drug ni 'gro drug gis skye
NK016(ma)001:871: sgo gcod cing lam phar phyin drug dang ldan zhing
NK016(ma)001:872: / 'bras bu ye shes lnga dbyings dang drug gam /
NK016(ma)001:874: zhabs bzhi ni tshad med pa bzhi'i chos kyi dbyings
NK016(ma)001:875: las mi bskyod cing thugs mi 'jigs pa bzhis rang
NK016(ma)001:876: gzhan gyis don rdzogs par mdzad pa'i rtags /
NK016(ma)001:877: rdo rje'i gshog pa gdeng pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:878: dbyings dang ye shes kyis thams cad la khyab pa'i mtha' gnyis su mi bying ba'i rtags /
NK016(ma)001:879: sku la bskal pa'i me 'bar ba ni /
NK016(ma)001:880: ye shes kyis nyams 'bar ba'i rtags /
NK016(ma)001:881: zhal gayasa dakara ba ni sku ste /
NK016(ma)001:882: gzung 'dzin nam dngos 'dzin gyis skyon mi mnga' bas /
NK016(ma)001:884: rnam thar gsum la mtshan ma med pa /
NK016(ma)001:885: g.yona damra ba ni gsung ste /
NK016(ma)001:886: gzhan don la chags pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:888: rnam thar ni smon pa med pa /
NK016(ma)001:889: dbus mthing nag sku dang mthuna pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:892: rnam thar ni stong pa nyid /
NK016(ma)001:893: mthing nag ni drag po'i gdul bya 'dul bar byed pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:894: phyag druga gisa gayasa kyis dang po na ye shesa kyi rdo rje rtse dgu pa bsnams pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:895: khams gsum sa dgu 'joms zhing theg pa dagu'am ye shes dgu la sbyor ba'i rtags /
NK016(ma)001:896: de ltar lhun grub ye shes la /
NK016(ma)001:898: bsam gtan gyis pha rol tu phyin pa dang sbyar /
NK016(ma)001:899: bar ma na rdo rje rtse lnga pa bsnams pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:900: 'khor ba'i sems can gyi don mdzad nas lam rgyud
NK016(ma)001:901: lnga'i dug lnga rtsad bcad nas ye shes lnga la
NK016(ma)001:902: sbyor ba'i rtags / de yang yar rtse yab /
NK016(ma)001:904: lte ba 'du 'bral med pa'i byang chub sems kun
NK016(ma)001:905: la khyab pa'i bdag nyid sbyin pa'i pha rol tu
NK016(ma)001:907: phyag mtshan de gnyis ni nang rtags phyir shar bas rtags de dag ye shes kyi phyag mtshan no //
NK016(ma)001:908: g.yona gyis dang po na me dapung bsnams pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:909: phyi rol tu bdud dang mu stegs bsregs cing /
NK016(ma)001:910: nang du khams gsum gyi dug gsum bsregs rtags /
NK016(ma)001:911: de yang nyon mongs pa'i bud shing ye shes kyis mes bsregs pas /
NK016(ma)001:912: nyon mongs pa'i mi non pas bzod pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa dang sbyar /
NK016(ma)001:913: 'di ni srid pa za byed kyi phyag mtshan no //
NK016(ma)001:914: bar ma na kha t+aam ka basnams pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:915: rgyal byed dpa' rtags kyis phyag mtshan ste /
NK016(ma)001:916: bdud kyi lag cha phrog nas phyag tu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)001:917: rtse gsum yod pa ni kun tu kyi sa'am /
NK016(ma)001:918: chos sku pad+ma can gyi sa'am longs sku /
NK016(ma)001:919: yi ge 'khor lo'i sa'am sprul sku ste /
NK016(ma)001:920: de ltar gsum mthar phyin te /
NK016(ma)001:921: sku gsum lhun rdzogs mtshon pa'am /
NK016(ma)001:922: dug gsum rtsad nas gcod pa'i rtags /
NK016(ma)001:923: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis sku gsung thugs la mnga' brnyes te /
NK016(ma)001:924: don de nyid rtsol pa med par lhun gyis grub
NK016(ma)001:925: pas brtson 'grus kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang
NK016(ma)001:926: sbyar / phyag tha ma gnyisa na ri raba lta bu'i phura pa dril ba ni /
NK016(ma)001:927: rgyal byed srid pa yongs sgrol gyi phyag mtshan ste /
NK016(ma)001:928: khams gsum dug gsum lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs kyis ngang du sgrol ba'i rtags /
NK016(ma)001:929: de yang khams gsum gyi nyon mongs pa rtsad nas bcad pa ste /
NK016(ma)001:930: shes rab kyis pha rol du phyin pa'am /
NK016(ma)001:931: 'khor ba ma spang thabs mkhas pas /
NK016(ma)001:932: thabs kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang sbyar /
NK016(ma)001:933: yang na rdo rje rtse dgu theg pa dgu /
NK016(ma)001:934: yig 'bru dgu phur pa don gyi lha dgu'i rang bzhin /
NK016(ma)001:935: rtse lnga ni ye shes lnga /
NK016(ma)001:936: yig 'bru lnga k+ai la ya rigs lnga'i rang bzhin /
NK016(ma)001:937: me dpung ni nyon mongs pa brgyad khri bsregs cing yig 'bru sngags thams cad /
NK016(ma)001:938: lha ni lha tshogs thams cad kyis rang bzhin /
NK016(ma)001:939: kha t+w+aam ni dug gsum 'joms pa'i yig 'bru gsum /
NK016(ma)001:940: lha k+ai la ya rigs gsum gyi rang bzhin /
NK016(ma)001:941: tha ma gnyis phur pa dril ba ni /
NK016(ma)001:942: me long ye shes kyis ma rig pa rtsad nas gcod pa /
NK016(ma)001:944: lha badz+ra k+ai la ya thugs kyis rang bzhin no //
NK016(ma)001:945: dbu skra kham nag gyen du bardzesa pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:948: de mtha' gnyis su ma nyal ba'i rtags su gyen du bardzesa pa /
NK016(ma)001:949: thugs chos sku spros pa dang bral ba'i rtags su zlum po /
NK016(ma)001:950: dbu re re la thod skam lnga lngasa brgyan pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:952: thugs ye shes lnga'i rtags su rigs lnga'i sangsa rgyas dbu la bzhugs pa ste /
NK016(ma)001:953: spyi gtsug tu mi bskyod pa sngo /
NK016(ma)001:955: rna ltag g.yas su rin 'byung ser /
NK016(ma)001:957: rna ltag g.yon par don grub ljang /
NK016(ma)001:958: de dag kyang mtshan dang dpe byad kyis sgeg pa /
NK016(ma)001:959: zhal spyir gzigs pas brgyan pa /
NK016(ma)001:960: zhal re re la spyan gsum gsum ste dgu /
NK016(ma)001:961: dbus ma gsum gyen du gzigs pa /
NK016(ma)001:962: don chos sku la dgongs pa'i rtags /
NK016(ma)001:963: g.yas pa gsum sdong mig phyag gis phur pa la gzigs pa /
NK016(ma)001:964: zhing bcu dbyings su sgrol ba /
NK016(ma)001:965: g.yon pa gsum yum la gzigs pa /
NK016(ma)001:966: yab yum gnyis su med pa'i rtags /
NK016(ma)001:967: de yang g.yas pa ni thabs kyis spyan /
NK016(ma)001:968: dbus ma'i gsum ye shes kyi spyan de yang dus gsum mkhyen pa'i rtags so //
NK016(ma)001:969: yang na spyan dgu sa dgu la gzigs pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:970: khro gnyer g.yas g.yon gnyis su lnga lnga ste bcu ni stobs bcu mnga' ba /
NK016(ma)001:971: khro gnyer dbus ma 'greng bu ste gyen du sgreng ba ni /
NK016(ma)001:972: mtha' gnyis su ma nyal ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:974: dug gsum zhal du gsol ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:975: zhal re re na mche ba bzhi re brtsigs pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:976: nyon mongs pa skye shi na rgas bzhi rtsad nas gcod pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:977: yang na mche ba dkar ba ni /
NK016(ma)001:978: chos sku la skyon gyis ma gos pa /
NK016(ma)001:979: rtsa ba dmar ba ni thugs rje chags pa /
NK016(ma)001:980: rtse mo rno ba ni gzung 'dzin dbyings su sgrol ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:983: dur khrod chas brgyad dang bcu drug ste /
NK016(ma)001:984: de la dpal chas brgyad la mnab pa'i rgyan gsum la /
NK016(ma)001:985: theg chen mchog gis rgyan ni /
NK016(ma)001:986: sku stod la glanga chen gyis rko rlon ya ba kor ba ni /
NK016(ma)001:987: ba yad nyo ba de'i sgra la drang na /
NK016(ma)001:988: ma rig pa'i rgyu 'bras gnas su dag pa'am /
NK016(ma)001:989: theg pa dgu thugs ye shes su dag pa'i rtags so //
NK016(ma)001:990: dpa' gtum za byed kyi rgyan ni /
NK016(ma)001:991: sku smad la stag lpagsa kyis sham thabas byas pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:992: pa ra ma rtsa ra ma zhes pa'i sgra las drang na /
NK016(ma)001:993: bdud dang mu stegs 'joms pa'i thugs rje dpa' gtum
NK016(ma)001:994: gyi phrin las kyi 'gro don la bshol ba med
NK016(ma)001:995: par mdzad pa'o // tshul khrims gos kyis rgyan ni /
NK016(ma)001:996: zhing lpagsa kyis sked da kris ni /
NK016(ma)001:997: nyan thos kyis tshul khrims dang /
NK016(ma)001:998: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:999: gsang sngags kyis dam tshig dang gsum dpal chen gyis thugs la rdzogs pa'am /
NK016(ma)001:1000: phyogs bcu'i zhing khams dbang du sdud pa'i rtags so //
NK016(ma)001:1001: thod rlon lnga bcu rtsa gciga gisa phreng ba se ral khara thogas pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:1003: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bsgom pa la dur khrod chas brgyad /
NK016(ma)001:1004: dkyil 'khor gyis mthar bkod pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:1005: rgyan du thogs pa gnyis las /
NK016(ma)001:1007: dur khrod kyis chas brgyad ni /
NK016(ma)001:1008: dur khrod na klu brgyad dbang che ste /
NK016(ma)001:1009: de bsdu na klu rigs lnga'am /
NK016(ma)001:1011: sbrul dakara po'i rgyal rigs ste dabu skra bcing pa dang sku la brgyan pa /
NK016(ma)001:1012: rje'u rigs ser po'i snyan cha byas pa /
NK016(ma)001:1013: bram ze'i rigs damra posa gdu gu byas pa /
NK016(ma)001:1014: dmangs rigs nag posa rkang rgyan byas pa /
NK016(ma)001:1015: yang na rgyal rigs dkar pos dbu skra bcing pa /
NK016(ma)001:1016: rje'u rigs ser pos snyan cha /
NK016(ma)001:1017: bram ze dmar pos 'gul pa dang dpung rgyan byas pa /
NK016(ma)001:1018: gdol pa ljang kus ske rag /
NK016(ma)001:1019: dmangs rigs nag pos phyag gdub dang zhabs gdub byas pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:1020: zhe sdang gnas su dag pa ste /
NK016(ma)001:1021: sku'i rgyan du yang yin la /
NK016(ma)001:1022: mnyen lcug 'khril ba'i yum gyis rang bzhin yin no //
NK016(ma)001:1024: don dam bcud kyis rgyan zhag gi zo risa mkhura
NK016(ma)001:1025: ba la snum chen gyis thig les brgyan pa ni
NK016(ma)001:1026: / zhag rus pa'i bcud yin pa ltar /
NK016(ma)001:1027: theg pa thams cad kyis bcud dam snying po gsang sngags yin pas /
NK016(ma)001:1029: thugs rje chags pa'i rgyan rak+ta'i thig le brang dang kha la brgyan pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:1030: rtogs pas bdag don la chags /
NK016(ma)001:1031: thugs rjes gzhan don la chags te /
NK016(ma)001:1032: chags gnyis mi gtong ba'i rtags so //
NK016(ma)001:1033: phrin las lhun gyi grub pa'i rgyan thal chen gyis tshom bu thal gong la brgyan pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:1034: 'dul ba'i phrin las kyi dregs bcan dbang du bsdu ba'i rtags so //
NK016(ma)001:1035: yang na chos thams cad bdag 'dzin dang bral zhing
NK016(ma)001:1036: theg pa chen po mtshon gsung kyang brtag par bya'o
NK016(ma)001:1037: // yang na byug pa'i rgyan gsum ni /
NK016(ma)001:1038: sangs rgyas kyis sa gsum non pa'i rtags yin zhes snying rje rol pa'i rgyud las bshad do //
NK016(ma)001:1039: thogs pa'i rgyan gnyis la tshogs bdag dur khrod kyis
NK016(ma)001:1040: rgyan yan lag gi tshig mdo rnams la kinga rus
NK016(ma)001:1041: la bzos pa'i phreng ba zhing rgyus kyis pheng lung
NK016(ma)001:1043: dur khrod bdag po bsgral ba'i rtags so //
NK016(ma)001:1044: dpung pa la thod pa ra ri dang khral khrol gyis brgyan pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:1045: da ltar gyis sangs rgyas te /
NK016(ma)001:1046: de ltar thod pa tshar gsum ni dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas kyis phrin las rtogs pa'i rtags so //
NK016(ma)001:1047: zhabsa rgyab ma gnyis gayasa brkyang pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:1048: thugsa rje chen posa 'gro ba'i don madzada pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1049: g.yona bskum pa ni shes raba kyis dbyingsa rtogsa kyang
NK016(ma)001:1050: mya ngan lasa 'adsa pa'i pa'i mtha'a lasa mi gansa
NK016(ma)001:1051: pa'o // yang na zhabs nang ma gnyis g.yas bskum
NK016(ma)001:1052: pa ni thugs rje chen pos 'gro ba'i don mdzad
NK016(ma)001:1053: pa'o // na yang / chos kyi dbyings las ma
NK016(ma)001:1054: g.yos shing 'khor ba'i mtha' mi gos pa'i rtags so
NK016(ma)001:1055: pa'o // na yang / // g.yon brkyang ba ni
NK016(ma)001:1056: thugs rje chen pos 'gro ba'i don mdzad na yang
NK016(ma)001:1057: chos kyi dbyings las ma g.yos pa'i rtags so //
NK016(ma)001:1058: yang na zhags bzhi 'dor thabs ni /
NK016(ma)001:1059: byams pa snying rje dga' ba btang snyoms bzhi'i rtags /
NK016(ma)001:1060: g.yas bskum pa shes rab kyis 'khor ba'i mtha' mi gnas pa /
NK016(ma)001:1061: g.yon brkyang pa thabs te mya ngan las 'das pa'i mthar mi gnas pa /
NK016(ma)001:1062: rgyab ma gnyis kyi g.yon bskum pa ni thabs kyis 'gro don mdzad kyang dbyings las ma g.yos pa /
NK016(ma)001:1063: g.yas cung zad brkyang pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:1064: 'khor ba'i mtha' ma spangs nyid ni ye shes kyis don mdzad pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1065: yum bskyed pa yanga lus dang grib ma'i tshul du
NK016(ma)001:1066: yaba grub na yum grub ste sku mdog yab dang
NK016(ma)001:1067: mthun pa zhal gciga chos nyid /
NK016(ma)001:1069: zhabs gnyis zhi gnas dang lhag mthong rnam par dag pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1070: gayasa kha t+w+aam ka yab la 'khyud pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:1071: dbyings kyis ye shes dang 'du 'bral med par thugs dam bskul ba /
NK016(ma)001:1072: g.yona thod khrag snying dang bcas pa yab la stobs pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:1073: khams gsum gyis nyon mongs pa'i rgyud sbyang ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:1074: thal ba'i tshom bu ma gtogs pa /
NK016(ma)001:1075: rgyan dang cha lugas yaba dang 'dra ba lasa /
NK016(ma)001:1076: yum chos dbyings spros bral mtshon pa'i rtags su /
NK016(ma)001:1077: gziga gi sham thabsa gshog pa meda pa /
NK016(ma)001:1078: thod skam gyis phreng ba yod pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1079: yab kyis thugas kara ye shes semsa dpa' ranga 'dra ba /
NK016(ma)001:1080: de'i thugsa kara rdo rje h'u dang bacasa pa bsgom pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:1081: thugs tsit+ta rin po che'i gur phub pa lta bu'i nang nas /
NK016(ma)001:1083: de'i steng du ye shes sems dpa' rdo rje gzhon
NK016(ma)001:1084: nu rang 'dra ba phyag mtshan dang rgyan med pa
NK016(ma)001:1086: de'i thugs kar nyi ma'i steng du rdo rje nag
NK016(ma)001:1087: po rtse dgu pa nas 'bras tsam gyis steng du
NK016(ma)001:1088: thugs ye shes 'od gsal ba mtshon pa'i h'u yig
NK016(ma)001:1089: 'bru dgu spus bris pa lta bu'i g.yas su 'khor
NK016(ma)001:1090: ba'o // yum gyisa thugsa kar b+han+d+ha de'i nanga du zla ba de'i steng du h'u lasa /
NK016(ma)001:1091: tip+ta tsakra ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u gisa g.yona du 'khora ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:1092: de ni bdag rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK016(ma)001:1093: phyogs bcu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:1094: mngal gyis bag chags sbyang ba'i phyir /
NK016(ma)001:1095: yab yum gnyis kyi mkha' gsang byin gyis brlabs te /
NK016(ma)001:1096: yab kyis gasnga gansa su ma lasa nyi ma'i dkyila 'khora gyi steng du /
NK016(ma)001:1097: rdo rje naga po rtse dagu pa'i lte ba la h'u /
NK016(ma)001:1100: yum gyi gasnga gansa su pam lasa pad+ma damra po 'adba ma brgyad pa /
NK016(ma)001:1101: ze'u 'bru la am damra pos matshana pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1103: yab kyis thugs ka nas 'oda zera 'phros pasa phyogsa
NK016(ma)001:1104: bcu'i sangsa rgyas thamsa cada bsdus nas ranga gi zhal
NK016(ma)001:1105: du zhugsa / sku'i dbyibsa su brgyud /
NK016(ma)001:1106: yab yum gnyis ma chagas thabsa kyis rola pa madzada pasa rdo rje sbum nas /
NK016(ma)001:1107: yum gyi mkha'a la phab ste /
NK016(ma)001:1108: byang chub sems kyi cha dang po bsgril ma bcur gyur te /
NK016(ma)001:1109: phyir 'phros pasa phyogsa skyongsa bcu'i gdan thog tu bab pa lasa /
NK016(ma)001:1110: khro bcu khra thabs dang bcas pa bskyed pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:1111: khro bo ni dpal chen po'i sprul pa ste /
NK016(ma)001:1113: phyogsa skyongs bcu zil gyis gnan nas /
NK016(ma)001:1114: sku stobs bcu rdzogs pa'i rtags /
NK016(ma)001:1115: khra thabs ni dbu brnyan du ma yod pas /
NK016(ma)001:1116: thabs thugs rje bsam gyis mi khyab pas /
NK016(ma)001:1117: dbu brgyan so so dang mthun pa'i sprul pa du mar shar nas 'gro don mdzad pa'i rtags so //
NK016(ma)001:1118: bye brag so so'i don rtags ni /
NK016(ma)001:1120: badz+ra rdo rje ste thugs sam ye shes so //
NK016(ma)001:1121: kro d+ha khro bo ste ye shes nyon mongs pa la khro ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:1124: ka ra h'u byed pa ces yon tan gyi sdud pa'am don byed pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1125: gardza gardza ni sgrogs shig sgrogs shig pa ste /
NK016(ma)001:1129: mtshan gyis khyad par so sor ma gtogs pa sngags kun de ltar du shes par bya'o //
NK016(ma)001:1130: madun du e khram gyis nyi zla dmar ser pho mo'i steng du /
NK016(ma)001:1131: khro bo chena po h'u madzada dang /
NK016(ma)001:1132: yum rdo rje sgra 'byin ma ste /
NK016(ma)001:1133: yang na h'u ka ra ni phrin las la mtshan du gsol ba ste /
NK016(ma)001:1134: gdul bya bsgral ba'i rnam par shes pa h'u du mdzad nas 'og min du sbar ba'i phyir ro //
NK016(ma)001:1135: yum ni chos kyi dbyings so //
NK016(ma)001:1136: rdo rje ni dbyings ye shes dbyer med pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1137: sgra 'byin ni chos thams cad stong pa nyid kyis sgra sgrogs pas /
NK016(ma)001:1138: lta ngan gyi tshogs 'jigs par byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK016(ma)001:1141: phaga gisa mgo can dang smrig bu'i mgo can ni /
NK016(ma)001:1142: gdul bya lta na steng nyi zla gza' skar gyis
NK016(ma)001:1143: 'khor na dregs pa de lta bu yod pa 'dul
NK016(ma)001:1144: ba'o // gdul byed ye shes ltar na /
NK016(ma)001:1145: phag gtsang sme med pa ltar /
NK016(ma)001:1146: 'gro don la blang dor med pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1147: smrig bu sgyu che ba ltar ye shes kyis 'gro ba 'dul mkhas pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1148: badz+ra kro d+ha 'bru gong dang mthun /
NK016(ma)001:1149: bi dza ya rnam par rgyal ba ste /
NK016(ma)001:1150: thugs ye shes bdud las rgyal ba mtshon no //
NK016(ma)001:1152: ha na ha na rgyob cig rgyob cig pa ste /
NK016(ma)001:1153: ye shes kyis nyon mongs pa 'joms pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1155: shar phyogsa su brgya byin dkar po pho mo'i steng du /
NK016(ma)001:1156: khro bo chen po rnam para rgyal ba dang /
NK016(ma)001:1157: yum rdo rje snyem ma ste /
NK016(ma)001:1158: yang na rnam par rgyal ba ni /
NK016(ma)001:1159: don la mtshan du gsol ba ste /
NK016(ma)001:1160: mtha' gnyis las rnam par rgyal ba'i phyir ro //
NK016(ma)001:1161: yum rdo rje ni dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med kyis mtshan no //
NK016(ma)001:1162: snyem ma ni dbyings la mnga' brnyes pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1163: sprul pa'i phra mena ma stag dang bya rgod kyis mgo can ni /
NK016(ma)001:1165: stag ni dpa' gtum za ba bzhin du /
NK016(ma)001:1166: thugs rje ye shes kyis gdul bya sgrol ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:1168: sems can gzhan gyis gsod pa'i ro la za ba bzhin du /
NK016(ma)001:1169: 'gro ba la snying rjes dge sdig gis chos ston cing 'phur rtsal che ba ltar /
NK016(ma)001:1170: lta spyod kyis 'gro ba'i nyon mongs gcod pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1171: gdul bya ltar dri za'i 'khor ni dregs pa stag
NK016(ma)001:1172: dang bya rgod kyis mgo can yod pa 'dul ba'o
NK016(ma)001:1174: ni la dan+da h'u ces pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:1176: thugs mtshan ste thugs ye shes kyis log rtog 'joms pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1177: da ha da ha h'u phata ni gsol cig gsol cig pa ste /
NK016(ma)001:1178: nyon mongs pa mi gnas pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1179: shara lhor me lha dmar ser pho mo'i steng du khro bo chena po dbyug sngon can dang /
NK016(ma)001:1180: yum rdo rje sder mo ste /
NK016(ma)001:1181: yang na dbyug pa sngon po ni phyag mtshan la mtshan du gsol ba ste /
NK016(ma)001:1182: rin po che'i dbyug pa sngon po bsnams yang gsungs /
NK016(ma)001:1183: rdo rje sder mo ni thugs rje'i mtshan te /
NK016(ma)001:1185: dbyings las ma g.yos par ye shes kyi gdul bya 'dzin pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1186: sprul pa'i phra mena ma gayaga dang bya rog gisa mgo can ni /
NK016(ma)001:1189: thugs rje ye shes ltar mthas mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:1190: bya rog ni 'khu khrig che zhing tshe gsum dran pa ltar /
NK016(ma)001:1191: thugs chos nyid dus gsum dbyer med pa la 'gro don 'char ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:1192: gdul bya ltar na shar lho me lha'i 'khor na
NK016(ma)001:1193: dregs pa can g.yag dang bya rog mgo can yod
NK016(ma)001:1194: pa 'dul ba'o // badz+ra kro d+ha 'bru mthun /
NK016(ma)001:1196: zhes gshin rje gshed ces gdul bya la btags pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1197: pa tsa pa tsa h'u phata ni chom shig chom shig pa ste /
NK016(ma)001:1198: gdul bya'i nyon mongs pa bsgyur ba ste /
NK016(ma)001:1199: khams gsum sems can gyi gshin rje dag gis rje bo bdud ru tra /
NK016(ma)001:1200: thugs rje ye shes kyis bcom pas gshed do //
NK016(ma)001:1201: lho phyogs su gshin rje pho mo sngon po'i steng
NK016(ma)001:1202: du khro bo chen po gshin rje gshed po dang
NK016(ma)001:1203: / yum dur khrod badga mo ste /
NK016(ma)001:1204: yang na gshin rje'i gdul bya'i mtshan ste /
NK016(ma)001:1205: las kyis gshin rje 'dul zhing de'i gshed du gyur pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1207: dbyings kyis ngang du gzung 'dzin rgud pas yon tan snang ba'am /
NK016(ma)001:1208: khams gsum chos nyid du sdud pa'i phyir ro //
NK016(ma)001:1209: sprul pa'i phra men ma sha ba dang 'uga pa'i mgo can ni /
NK016(ma)001:1211: sha ba'i mgo la ru lag bcu yod cing 'jug pa cis kyang mi zlog pa ltar /
NK016(ma)001:1212: thugs ye shes dbyings las 'jug pas cis kyang mi bzlog ste /
NK016(ma)001:1213: sa bcu stobs bcu lhun gyi grub pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1215: mtshan yang shing mig rno ba ltar /
NK016(ma)001:1216: thugs ye shes kyis dbyings su mi 'byed par 'gro ba ma rig pa'i rgyud mkhyen cing gsal ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:1218: gshin rje'i 'khor na dregs pa sha ba dang 'ug pa'i mgo can yod pa 'dul ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:1222: thugs gzung 'dzin gyis mi g.yo ba'i mtshan no //
NK016(ma)001:1223: b+han+d+ha b+hana d+ha h'u phata ni chings shig chings shig pa ste /
NK016(ma)001:1224: ye shes kyis gzung 'dzin 'gro 'ong rgyun gcod pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1225: lho nub tu srin po pho mo dmar nag gis steng du khro bo mi g.yo mgona po dang /
NK016(ma)001:1226: yum rdo rje gtun khung ma ste /
NK016(ma)001:1227: yang na mi g.yo mgon po ni /
NK016(ma)001:1228: don la mtshan du gsol ba ste /
NK016(ma)001:1229: mtha' gnyis kyi rlung gis mi g.yo zhing 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa'i phyir ro //
NK016(ma)001:1232: chos nyid kyi ngang du chos can gyis mtshan ma zad par mdzad pa'i phyir ro //
NK016(ma)001:1233: sprul pa gzig dang kha t+wa'i mgo can ni /
NK016(ma)001:1235: gzig tshang bsil zhing dran pa rgod pa yin ste /
NK016(ma)001:1236: thugs kyi ngang ma gtogs bar mi gnas zhing gdul bya'i rgyud mkhyen pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1237: kha t+wa la sgrib shing yod pas tshang mi mthong ba ltar /
NK016(ma)001:1238: thugs ye shes dpag dka' ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:1240: lho nub srin po'i 'khor na dregs pa gzig dang kha t+wa'i mgo can yod pas de 'dul ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:1242: h+ya g+r+ai ba h'u ni rta mgrin ste /
NK016(ma)001:1243: thugs ye shes 'gro don du mgyog cing shugs che ba'i rtags su rta dbu la btags pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1244: hu lu hu lu h'u phata ni /
NK016(ma)001:1245: lkug par gyis shig lkug pa gyis shig pa ste /
NK016(ma)001:1246: nyon mongs pa can gyis dran pa nyams par gyis shig pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1247: nub tu klu dmar po pho mo'i steng du /
NK016(ma)001:1248: khro bo chen po rta mgrin dang /
NK016(ma)001:1249: yum rdo rje gtum mo ste /
NK016(ma)001:1251: rtags la mtshan du gsol ba ste /
NK016(ma)001:1252: bdud dang srin po 'dul ba'i phyir /
NK016(ma)001:1253: dbu la rta dbu ljang ku mnga' ba'i phyir ro //
NK016(ma)001:1254: yum rdo rje gtum mo ni /
NK016(ma)001:1257: nyon mongs pa btsan thabs su gcod pa'i phyir ro //
NK016(ma)001:1259: pu shud kyis mgo can ni /
NK016(ma)001:1261: byi la ni mkhas shing gzob ltar /
NK016(ma)001:1262: ye shes kyi dbyings kyi don rtogs pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:1264: pu shud la mig rtsi dang ze ba yod pa ltar /
NK016(ma)001:1265: ye shes kyi ma rig pa'i mun pa sel zhing /
NK016(ma)001:1266: thugs mtha' gnyis kyi skyon dang bral bas ze ba yod pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1268: nub chu lho'i 'khor na dregs pa can byi la
NK016(ma)001:1269: dang pu shud kyis mgo can yod pa 'dul ba'o
NK016(ma)001:1271: a pa r+aa dzi ta h'u ni /
NK016(ma)001:1272: gzhan gyi mi thub pa ste /
NK016(ma)001:1273: thugs ye shes kyis gdul bya bdud dang srin po las rgyal ba'i rtags so //
NK016(ma)001:1274: tish+tha tish+tha h'u phata ni non cig non cig pa ste /
NK016(ma)001:1275: ye shes kyis ma rig pa'i stobs non pa ste /
NK016(ma)001:1276: rtags bdud dang dregs pa zil gyis gnan pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1277: nub byang du rlung lha pho mo sngo skya'i steng
NK016(ma)001:1278: du khro bo chen po gazhana gyi mi thub pa
NK016(ma)001:1279: dang / yum rdo rje mda' bsnyem ma ste /
NK016(ma)001:1280: yang na gzhan gyis mi thub pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:1281: gnyen po la mtshan du gsol ba ste /
NK016(ma)001:1282: mtha' gnyis kyi skyon gyis mi shigs pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1284: rig pa'i mdas nyon mongs pa 'big pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1285: dbyings snyan bral du gnas pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1286: yang na rig pa'i ye shes kyis mdas chod nyid kyi ngang du bstim pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1287: sprul pa spyang ku dang khra'i mgo can ni /
NK016(ma)001:1289: spyang ku ni 'dzin gsod za ba ltar /
NK016(ma)001:1290: thugs chod nyid zab mo rtogs pas /
NK016(ma)001:1291: dge sdig mnyam par rtogs pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1292: khra ni gzan tshol ba rnyed nas thog med du gsod pa ltar /
NK016(ma)001:1293: ye shes kyis gdul bya gzigs te sgrol ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:1295: rlung lha'i 'khor na dregs pa can spyang ku dang /
NK016(ma)001:1296: khra'i mgo can yod pa 'dul ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:1298: a mri ta kun+da li h'u ni /
NK016(ma)001:1299: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa zhes bya ste /
NK016(ma)001:1300: gnyen pos nyon mongs pa rnams ye shes kyi rtsis bsgyur dbyings su sgrol ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:1301: tshin+d+ha tshin+d+ha h'u phata ni chod cig chod cig pa ste /
NK016(ma)001:1302: ye shes kyis nyon mongs pa'i rtsal gcod pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1303: byang phyogs su gnong sbyin pho mo ljang ser gyi
NK016(ma)001:1304: steng du khro bo chen po bdud rtsi 'khyil pa
NK016(ma)001:1305: dang / yum rdo rje rlung 'byin ma ste /
NK016(ma)001:1306: yang na bdud rtsi 'khyil pa ni yon tan la mtshan du gsol ba ste /
NK016(ma)001:1307: mtha' gnyis kyi bdud dbyings dang ye shes kyi rtsis chos kyi skur bskyil ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:1309: gdul bya la thugs rje rlung lta bus dbyings su bskyed par byed pa'am /
NK016(ma)001:1310: 'khor ba'i bag chags rdul dang 'dra ba ye shes
NK016(ma)001:1311: kyi rlung gis gtor nas mya ngan las 'das par
NK016(ma)001:1314: pha wam gisa mgo can ni /
NK016(ma)001:1317: sgra sgrags pa tsam gyis gcan gzan gzhan brgyal zhing zil gyis gnon pa ltar /
NK016(ma)001:1318: dpal chen po'i thugs ye shes kyis nyon mongs pa
NK016(ma)001:1319: dang lta ba ngan pa thams cad zil gyis non
NK016(ma)001:1320: pa'am / thugs ye shes a ti yo gas theg dman zil gyis gnon pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1324: thugs yang dag pa'i ye shes kyis gdul bya 'dren cing chos skur sbyor ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:1326: byang phyogs gnod sbyin gyi 'khor na dregs pas seng+ge
NK016(ma)001:1327: dang pha wam gis mgo can yod pa de dag
NK016(ma)001:1329: tree lo kya bi dza ya h'u ni /
NK016(ma)001:1330: 'jig rten gsum las rgyal ba ste /
NK016(ma)001:1331: thugs yang dag pa'i ye shes kyis srid gsum gyi rtog pa las rgyal ba las btags pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1333: phug cig phug cig pa ste /
NK016(ma)001:1334: thugs ye shes kyi nyon mongs pa sra mkhregs te phug pa ste /
NK016(ma)001:1336: byang shar du dbang ldan pho mo ser po'i steng du /
NK016(ma)001:1337: khro bo chen po khamas gsum rnam par rgyal ba dang /
NK016(ma)001:1338: yum rdo rje gsoda byed ma ste /
NK016(ma)001:1339: yang na khams gsum rnam par rgyal ba ni /
NK016(ma)001:1340: spang bya las mtshan du gsol ba ste /
NK016(ma)001:1341: khams gsum dug gsum lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs su shar bas /
NK016(ma)001:1342: de dag gis skyon las rnam par rgyal ba'i phyir ro //
NK016(ma)001:1344: 'khor ba'i rtog pa dbyings su gsod pa'am /
NK016(ma)001:1345: mtha' gnyis kyi nyes pa ma gos pas /
NK016(ma)001:1346: dbyings ye shes rang byung gis ye shes kyis gsod pa'i phyir ro //
NK016(ma)001:1347: sprul pa dom dang sre mong gisa mgo can ni /
NK016(ma)001:1349: dom rmi lam rmis na cis kyang mi bzlog cing gsod pa ltar /
NK016(ma)001:1350: thugs ye shes kyi gdul bya la gzigs nas phrin las kyi sgrol ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:1351: sre mong ni mgyog cing myur ba ltar /
NK016(ma)001:1352: 'gro don du thugs ye shes cir yang 'char zhing 'gyur du btub bo //
NK016(ma)001:1354: byang shar dbang ldan gyi 'khor na dregs pa dom
NK016(ma)001:1355: dang sre mong gis mgo can yod pa 'dul ba'o
NK016(ma)001:1357: ma h+aa ba la h'u ni stobs po che ste /
NK016(ma)001:1358: thugs ye shes kyi stobs kyis 'khor ba sangs rgyas kyis sar 'degs pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1359: s+pho ta s+pho ta h'u phata ni /
NK016(ma)001:1360: gzir cig gzer cig pa ste /
NK016(ma)001:1361: thugs ye shes kyis nyon mongs pa gzer bya'o //
NK016(ma)001:1362: nub tu sa bdag pho mo dud kha'i steng du khro bo chen po stobsa po che dang /
NK016(ma)001:1363: yum rdo rje bskul byed ma ste /
NK016(ma)001:1364: yang na stobs po che ni /
NK016(ma)001:1365: stobs la mtshan du gsol ba ste /
NK016(ma)001:1366: chos thams cad dbyings dang ye shes kyis stobs las shar ba'i phyir ro //
NK016(ma)001:1368: dbyings kyi thugs rjes 'khor ba yang dag pa'i don la bskul ba'am /
NK016(ma)001:1369: yang na dus gsum bder gshegs kyis phrin las thugs
NK016(ma)001:1370: rje 'gro ba drug gis don du bskul zhing 'gro
NK016(ma)001:1371: drug mya ngan las 'das pa'i sa la bskul ba'i
NK016(ma)001:1372: phyir ro // sprul pa dred dang /
NK016(ma)001:1373: byi ba'i mgo can no ni /
NK016(ma)001:1375: dred ni stobs ldan pra rno ba ltar /
NK016(ma)001:1376: yang dag pa'i ye shes kyis gdul bya'i rgyud mkhyen te dus gcig tu sgrol ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:1379: rku ba'i sgo mar du dod pa ltar /
NK016(ma)001:1380: thugs ye shes kyis don thar lam gyis sgo bsam gyis mi khyab par mkhyen pa'i rtags so //
NK016(ma)001:1382: 'og phyogs sa bdag gi 'khor na dregs pa dred
NK016(ma)001:1383: dang byi ba'i mgo can yod pa de 'dul ba'i
NK016(ma)001:1384: phyir ro // khro bo ni ngang khro ye shes /
NK016(ma)001:1385: shugs khro thugs rjes nyon mongs pa bcom pa ste /
NK016(ma)001:1386: rtags dpal chen po dregs pa can 'dul bas khro tshul bcas te /
NK016(ma)001:1387: thugs la khro ba mdzad de /
NK016(ma)001:1388: sku khro ba dang bcas pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1389: phyogs skyongs bcu non cing mi dge ba stobs bcus bcom pa'i phyir bcu yanga 'byung la /
NK016(ma)001:1390: kun kyang 'dra bar zhal gciga rang byung ye shes /
NK016(ma)001:1392: sku mdoga mthing nag ni thugs chos nyid la 'gyur ba med pa'i rtags /
NK016(ma)001:1393: phyag na phur pa dril ba ni /
NK016(ma)001:1394: thugs ye shes rtse gcig gis gzung 'dzin 'big pa /
NK016(ma)001:1395: zhabsa gnyis brkyang bskum gyis phyogsa skyongsa la bardzisa pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:1396: 'gro drug gis nyon mongs pa gnyis 'dzin 'jom pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1397: yang na zhal gsum phyag drug tu bsgom gsungs /
NK016(ma)001:1398: rdo rje'i gshogas pa gdenga ba /
NK016(ma)001:1399: sku la dpal chen po'i chasa dang /
NK016(ma)001:1400: dur khrod chen po'i chas sogs rgyan rnamasa gtso bo dang mthun /
NK016(ma)001:1401: yum khro mo ni dbyings kyi shes rab kyis gdul bya 'dul ba ste /
NK016(ma)001:1402: thams cada 'khora lo rgyas 'debsa ma dang mthun no //
NK016(ma)001:1403: khro bo rnams kyi thugs kar h'u la rang rang gis sngags kyis 'khor bar bsam /
NK016(ma)001:1405: rtags yab yum thabs shes las sprul pa'i khra thabas sam phra men ni /
NK016(ma)001:1406: don dbyings ye shes las byung ba'i rtags su /
NK016(ma)001:1407: mgo lus mi mtshams pa'i phra men te /
NK016(ma)001:1408: dpe gser g.yu'i phra lta bu /
NK016(ma)001:1409: kun mthing nag mgo brnyan can phyag gnyis pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1410: stag mgo can la sogas pa'i yab rnams kyis gtso bo la gzigs pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1411: phyag gayasa na ranga ranga gisa mgo brnyan dang mthun
NK016(ma)001:1412: pa'i semsa can re re khra ru 'gyed pa bsnamsa
NK016(ma)001:1413: pa po / g.yona pa rnams kyis phur pa bsnamsa nas yum gyis gru mo nas 'khyud pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1414: bya mgo can rnams kyi yab la gzigs shing /
NK016(ma)001:1415: phyag gnyis kasa rang rang gisa mgo brnyan dang mthun pa'i bya re re spyi bor bsnamsa pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1416: 'o na smrig bu sre mong byi la gsum phra men yin nam ce na /
NK016(ma)001:1417: smrig bu sre mong gnyis gshogs pa med kyang sgong nga las skyes pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1418: byi ba la ni mtshan mor rgyu bas /
NK016(ma)001:1419: stong pa shes rab kyis don mtshon pa yin gsung /
NK016(ma)001:1420: sku stod la chu srin gyis stod g.yoga ni /
NK016(ma)001:1421: kha gnyis na phyir lasa pa gnyisa byung ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:1422: zhing lpagsa kyis rked chingas stag lpagsa kyis sham thabsa can /
NK016(ma)001:1423: dbu la thod rlon gsum gsum gyis brgyan pa /
NK016(ma)001:1424: yan lag dang sku la sbrul gyis bargyan pa /
NK016(ma)001:1425: yab kyis zhabs g.yas zhing gis mkhur ba /
NK016(ma)001:1427: yum gyi zhabs g.yas rtsib sgang /
NK016(ma)001:1428: g.yon pus mo la bardzisa pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1430: yab yum gyi kha barlanga gi tshul du bskyed gsungs /
NK016(ma)001:1431: yang na thur pa dpal 'bar khro bo'i rgyud na gdul bya'i snang ba la dgongs te /
NK016(ma)001:1432: rdo rje gzhon nus ru tra bsgral bas mi dge
NK016(ma)001:1433: ba bcu'i ngo bo snying khrag la phyogs skyong pho
NK016(ma)001:1434: mo grub / de grub pa'i khro bo yab yum nyi shur sprul nas phyogs skyong pho mo bsgral /
NK016(ma)001:1435: de dag gis snying khrag thig re la /
NK016(ma)001:1437: bya mgo can re re ste nyi shur sprul te /
NK016(ma)001:1439: khro bo yab yum la za byed gsod byed rnams sprul te /
