NK016(ma)001:1440: dregs pa de dag bsgral bar bshad /
NK016(ma)001:1443: stobs bcu la sogs pa dang sbyar /
NK016(ma)001:1444: yum bcu ni pha rol tu phyin pa bcu dang sbyar /
NK016(ma)001:1445: za byed bcu ni bdag don rtogs pa'i ye shes dang /
NK016(ma)001:1447: phrin las la sogs te dgongs pa'i yon tan dang sbyar /
NK016(ma)001:1449: 'du byed lnga bcu rtsa gcig gis nang na chos
NK016(ma)001:1450: mthun pa bcu gnas su dag pa dang sbyar ste
NK016(ma)001:1451: / sems pa gnas su dag pa bya rgod mgo can /
NK016(ma)001:1452: 'dun pa gnas su gyur pa bya rog mgo can /
NK016(ma)001:1453: yid la byed pa gnas su gyur pa 'ug pa'i mgo can /
NK016(ma)001:1454: ting nge 'dzin gnas su gyur pa kha t+wa'i mgo can /
NK016(ma)001:1455: dad pa gnas su gyur pa pu shud mgo can /
NK016(ma)001:1456: mos pa gnas su gyur pa khra'i mgo can /
NK016(ma)001:1457: dran pa gnas su gyur pa pha wam mgo can /
NK016(ma)001:1458: shes rab gnas su gyur pa sre mong mgo can /
NK016(ma)001:1459: gnyid gnas su gyur pa smrig bu'i mgo can /
NK016(ma)001:1460: de dag gi gnas skabs kyi bye brag gnas su gyur pa ni byi ba'i mgo can no //
NK016(ma)001:1461: mdor na sems dang sems byung gis chos thams cad dbyings dang ye shes su gnas su gyur pas /
NK016(ma)001:1462: dbyings dang ye shes kyis byin rlabs sam rtags su phra men ma rnams su snang la /
NK016(ma)001:1463: gzhan yang sprul pa bye ba drug cu'am /
NK016(ma)001:1464: bye ba brgya rtsa gcig ni /
NK016(ma)001:1466: lcags kyis lpags pa can dang /
NK016(ma)001:1467: zangs kyis lpags pa can dang /
NK016(ma)001:1468: mchu rdo rje gzung can la sogs pa'i sprul pa
NK016(ma)001:1469: dang yang sprul dang bcas pa'i phyogs bcu bar mtshams
NK016(ma)001:1470: med par gtam nas yod pa /
NK016(ma)001:1471: de dag kyang sems dang sems byung gnas su dag pa ste /
NK016(ma)001:1472: dbyings dang ye shes las sprul pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1473: phur pa sras kyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK016(ma)001:1474: lag pa g.yas g.yon sor mo bsnol nas /
NK016(ma)001:1475: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba b+hig+hana bam h'u phata ces brjod pa tsam gyis /
NK016(ma)001:1476: yang gtso bo yab yum gyis gasnga gansa nas h'u nyi shu rtsa gciga spros te /
NK016(ma)001:1477: gru gsum gyi kha la phoga ngosa gsum du bduna
NK016(ma)001:1478: bduna ste nyer gcig ni logs gsum du drug drug
NK016(ma)001:1479: zur tsam gsum du gsum ste /
NK016(ma)001:1480: de 'oda du zhu ba lasa sras mchoga zhal gciga phyag gnyisa pa /
NK016(ma)001:1481: sku mdoga mthing nag rgyan meda pa /
NK016(ma)001:1482: phyag na phur pa dril ba /
NK016(ma)001:1483: dbu skra kham pa gyen du bardzesa pa ma bcinga pa /
NK016(ma)001:1484: lte ba man chada gnam lcagsa kyi phur pa dmar zang ngera 'duga pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1485: yang na phur pa khrag 'thung drug cu rtsa gnyis
NK016(ma)001:1486: kyis dkyil 'khor bskyed pa 'di yang skye gnas sbyang
NK016(ma)001:1487: ba yin te / gtso bo ni h'u la sogs
NK016(ma)001:1488: cho ga gsum gyi bskyed pas drod gsher la skye
NK016(ma)001:1489: ba yin te / ba sbyang / ye shes sems dpa' bardzusa skyes su bskyed pas bardzusa skyes sbyang /
NK016(ma)001:1490: khro bo yab yum h'u kha sbyor 'od sgong nga lta bu bskyed pas sgong skyes sbyang /
NK016(ma)001:1491: sras mchog nyer gcig la yum gyis mkha' nas bskyed pas mngal skyes sbyang ces 'dod pa snang ngo //
NK016(ma)001:1492: dam can srung ma'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK016(ma)001:1493: lha snam gyis dam can bcu gnyis kyi shwa na bzhi ni /
NK016(ma)001:1494: dpal chen po'i gsung gis rnam par 'phrul par snang
NK016(ma)001:1495: zhing gsung gis phrin las thams cad thogs pa med
NK016(ma)001:1496: par bsgrub cing / dgra bgegs kyis ngag rdul du brlag pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1498: dpal chen po'i sku'i rnam par 'phrul par snang zhing sku'i phrin las thogs pa med par sgrub cing /
NK016(ma)001:1499: dgra bgegs kyis lus rdul du brlag pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1501: dpal chen po'i thugs kyi rnam par 'phrul par snang
NK016(ma)001:1502: zhing thugs dgongs pa'i phrin las thams cad thogs pa
NK016(ma)001:1504: dgra bgegs kyis yid rdul du brlag par mdzad pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1505: re mdzu'i pha bdud rkang rje drang dkar /
NK016(ma)001:1506: ma bdud srog len hab sha ma /
NK016(ma)001:1507: re ma ti'i pha bdud pad+ma gar gyis dbang phyug /
NK016(ma)001:1508: ma bdud mo brgya byin kun dga' mo /
NK016(ma)001:1509: re mdzi'i pha bdud thod pa'i phreng ba can /
NK016(ma)001:1510: ma bdud mo e ka tsa ti ma /
NK016(ma)001:1511: re ma dza'i pha bdud srin po ma ti ka /
NK016(ma)001:1512: ma bdud mo gling bzhi kun 'byams ma'o //
NK016(ma)001:1513: de ltar pho bdud nyi shu rtsa gcig na /
NK016(ma)001:1516: ri ma ti bzhi dang bcu gnyis /
NK016(ma)001:1517: nag mo chen mo glog phreng ma /
NK016(ma)001:1518: sa bdag nag mo ral gcig ma /
NK016(ma)001:1519: mgo med brang ni mig gis khengs ma /
NK016(ma)001:1520: lcags kyi spyad mo mgo dgu ma dang bzhi ni /
NK016(ma)001:1521: bse mo bzhi'i blon po yin yang zer /
NK016(ma)001:1523: dngul gyis ba rgod dung mgo can /
NK016(ma)001:1524: lcags kyis bya rgod kha tong mchu /
NK016(ma)001:1525: zangs kyi re 'byams mgo dgu ma /
NK016(ma)001:1526: gser gyis bya rgod rgya mgo ma dang bzhi ni pho nya yin skad /
NK016(ma)001:1529: skem ma chu srin gyi mgo can ste /
NK016(ma)001:1530: re ma ti bzhi'i pho nya yin skad /
NK016(ma)001:1531: mo bdud nyi shu phyi'i las mkhan yin zer ba yang yod skad /
NK016(ma)001:1532: de ltar mo'i 'khor nyi khri gcig stong ngo //
NK016(ma)001:1533: dam can bcu gnyis ni bya nag thang la bab pa ltar bskyed gsungs /
NK016(ma)001:1534: gazhala yasa khanga gisa phyi rol rdo rje rwa ba'i nang rol du /
NK016(ma)001:1535: shar nas brtsam te g.yas bskor du /
NK016(ma)001:1540: baswe'i skyes bu gdug pa can bzhi /
NK016(ma)001:1542: 'byung po sera po sna yon dang nyi shu rtsa
NK016(ma)001:1543: gciga byang shar mtshams la ma thugs bar la 'khora
NK016(ma)001:1544: bar yoda pa mos pa tsam bya ste /
NK016(ma)001:1545: de la pho bdud kyis mtshan mi 'dra ba mang du btags pa yod kyang /
NK016(ma)001:1550: dur khrod bdag po dang bzhi ni /
NK016(ma)001:1551: re ma ti bzhi'i ming po yin skad /
NK016(ma)001:1553: tshangs pa dkar po dung gis thor gtsug can /
NK016(ma)001:1556: nag po phya sang dang bzhi ni /
NK016(ma)001:1557: shwa na bzhi'i ming po yin skad /
NK016(ma)001:1562: klu tag sha ka dang bzhi ni /
NK016(ma)001:1563: shwa na bzhi'i bka' nyan yin skad /
NK016(ma)001:1564: bswe'i skyes bu gdug pa can bzhi ni /
NK016(ma)001:1566: gshin rje me ru rtse dang /
NK016(ma)001:1567: gnod sbyin me ru rtse dang /
NK016(ma)001:1568: srin po me ru rtse dang bzhi ni /
NK016(ma)001:1569: bswe mo bzhi'i ming po yin skad /
NK016(ma)001:1572: klu gdengs po snying dkar dang /
NK016(ma)001:1574: gza' mig dmar dang bzhi ni /
NK016(ma)001:1575: bswe mo bzhi'i pha yin skad /
NK016(ma)001:1576: de bzhi la ni bdud bzhi yin zer ba yang yod skad /
NK016(ma)001:1581: bdud mo 'dzum med ma dang bzhi yin skad /
NK016(ma)001:1582: 'byung po ser po sna yon ni /
NK016(ma)001:1583: tshogs bdag glang sna yin skad /
NK016(ma)001:1584: de'i bka' nyan gnam gyi ma sang skyes gcig yin skad /
NK016(ma)001:1585: de ltar 'jig rten gyi las mkhan pho nya dgu bcu gsum mo //
NK016(ma)001:1588: de'i phyi rol tu ging pho dgu mo dgu rnams
NK016(ma)001:1589: gtso bo la mos pa'i tshul du 'dud par bsam
NK016(ma)001:1590: / dngos su phyag mtshan gsal bar bsgom na bkra mi shis ces gsungs /
NK016(ma)001:1591: spyi don drug pa ye shes kyis dkyil 'khor gzhugs pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:1592: sa man dzas snyan gsan dbab nas /
NK016(ma)001:1593: thugs ka nas 'od zer kha dog sna lnga 'phros
NK016(ma)001:1594: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyis zhing khams thams cad la
NK016(ma)001:1595: phog / sangs rgyas thams cad chos sku la gzugs
NK016(ma)001:1596: skur bzhengs nas kun kyang rdo rje gzhon nu'i dkyil
NK016(ma)001:1597: 'khor rig 'dzin bla ma dang bcas pa rnams kyi
NK016(ma)001:1598: rnam par bzhugs par bsam la /
NK016(ma)001:1599: ja 'dren gyi tshul du rnam lnga 'bul la /
NK016(ma)001:1600: rda la sogs pa rol mo'i bye brag rnams bskrol brdung bya ste /
NK016(ma)001:1602: ye shes kyis chos skyong bya rog gdong can gyis /
NK016(ma)001:1603: da lta cha 'ur gyis bskrol brdung byas na dga' ces pa'i lo rgyus bzhin no //
NK016(ma)001:1604: lha la mchod pa 'bul ba'i phyir dang /
NK016(ma)001:1605: tha mal gyi rtogs pa zil gyi gnon pa'i phyir dang /
NK016(ma)001:1606: bar do'i sgra 'od zer gsum sbyang ba'i phyir du'o //
NK016(ma)001:1608: ye shes dbyings kyi rnga brdung dang /
NK016(ma)001:1609: sgrub pa las kyi rnga brdung dang /
NK016(ma)001:1610: tshar gsum pa'i rnga brdung la sogs pa rnams kyi don dang /
NK016(ma)001:1611: spyan 'dren dang lhag ma yan chad kyis rnga dil rnams /
NK016(ma)001:1612: pad 'byung gis rnga brdung rin chen phreng ba dang /
NK016(ma)001:1613: gnyan rgod ston pa'i rnga brdung rnams de ltar shes par bya zhing /
NK016(ma)001:1618: ro long nag po'i mthing rdung la sogs pa rnams byas la /
NK016(ma)001:1619: tshig bdun pas bla ma spyan 'dren la bstim /
NK016(ma)001:1620: de nas yi dam la 'phyong drug gis sgo nas spyan 'dren te /
NK016(ma)001:1621: de yang gdul byed ye shes kyis 'phyong gsum dang /
NK016(ma)001:1622: gdul bya yul gyi 'phyong gsum mo //
NK016(ma)001:1624: ye ma bcos pa chos dbyings kyi rang rig pa'i shes rab kyis rtogs nas /
NK016(ma)001:1625: dbyings dang rig pa gnyis su med pa de la ye shes ces bya'o //
NK016(ma)001:1626: phur bu ni dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med kyis
NK016(ma)001:1627: don de nyid bsgrub pa ni mchog gis dngos grub
NK016(ma)001:1628: / de'i zhor la thun mong gis grub pa brgyad lta bu grub pa'i phyir dang /
NK016(ma)001:1629: 'khor 'das kyis chos la dabnga byed cing mchog dang
NK016(ma)001:1630: thun mong gi dngosa grub rnams blang ba ni dkyil
NK016(ma)001:1632: bsgrub pa po la stsol ba'i phyir /
NK016(ma)001:1633: dama tshiga chen po ni dpal rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum ste /
NK016(ma)001:1634: 'khor ba ma stong gis bar du gdul bya'i don
NK016(ma)001:1635: mdzad pa las mi 'da' bas dam tshig chen po'o
NK016(ma)001:1636: // de nyid don ngo bo la gshegs bzhugs mi mnga' yang /
NK016(ma)001:1637: gdul bya'i ngo la gnas 'dir gshegas su gsola /
NK016(ma)001:1638: de lta bu'i rdo rje gzhona nu yab yum gshegas nas kyang ci mdzad ce na /
NK016(ma)001:1639: grub sems pa'i rtagsa dang grub zin pa'i matshana ma'am /
NK016(ma)001:1640: yang na dngos grub kyis mtshan ma dang /
NK016(ma)001:1641: sgrol bya sgrol ba'i rtags so //
NK016(ma)001:1642: de dag mngon sum du bstan pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:1643: k+ai la ya ni dbyings ye shes kyis dngos grub bam /
NK016(ma)001:1644: mchog thun mong gis dngosa grub stsol cig ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:1645: ye shes phur bu dabnga dang 'bru mthun /
NK016(ma)001:1646: dpal rdo rje gzhon nu'i thugs gnyis su med pa'i
NK016(ma)001:1647: ye shes thabs thugs rje la sprul pa'i khro bo
NK016(ma)001:1648: bcu dang dbyings shes rab las sprul pa'i khro mo
NK016(ma)001:1649: bcu ste / gzhan las khyad par du gyur pas chen po gshegas su gsol /
NK016(ma)001:1650: bdud dang log 'dren las rgyal bas khro rgyal yab yuma nyi shu gshegas nasa kyang /
NK016(ma)001:1651: rtagsa dang k+ai la ya'i 'bru mthun /
NK016(ma)001:1652: ye shes phur bu dabnga dang khro bo rnams kyi mngag gzhug gis pho nya yin pa'i phyir /
NK016(ma)001:1653: phyag brnyan chen po gshegsa su gsola /
NK016(ma)001:1654: don nyon mongs pa ma spangs bar thabs sna tshogs kyis sgo nas gcod cing /
NK016(ma)001:1655: rtags sems can rnams phyag mtshan du khra ru 'gyed
NK016(ma)001:1656: thabs su bsnams pa'i yab yum nyi shu gshegsa nas
NK016(ma)001:1657: kyang / rtagsa dang k+ai la ya'i gnyis pa gdul bya yul 'dzin pa'i 'phyong ni /
NK016(ma)001:1658: srid pa ni kun nas nyon mongs pa 'khor ba'i chos te /
NK016(ma)001:1659: khams gsum dang lus ngag yid gsum mo //
NK016(ma)001:1663: ye shes kyi mkha' 'gro spyang ku'i gdong pa can la sogs ste /
NK016(ma)001:1664: sha za'i chos lugs gdong pa can bzhi gshegas su gsola /
NK016(ma)001:1665: de lta bu'i shwa na mcheda bzhi gshegsa nasa kyang /
NK016(ma)001:1666: rtagsa dang k+ai la ya'i dngosa grub stsol /
NK016(ma)001:1669: ye shes kyi lha la mchog thun mong gis dngos grub kyis gsol ba gdab pa yin te /
NK016(ma)001:1670: dam tshig la grub pa chen po brgyad man chad /
NK016(ma)001:1671: las phran tshogs kyis dngos grub yan chad gsol ba gdab pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1672: srid pa'i dabnga dang gling bzhi'am 'byung ba bzhi'i bdag mo bswe mo bzhi yin pas /
NK016(ma)001:1673: sa badga chen mo gshegas su gsol /
NK016(ma)001:1674: de lta bu'i 'dzam gling gis bswe shing yod pa'i
NK016(ma)001:1675: gnas na bzhugs pa'i bswe mo mched bzhi gshegas nasa
NK016(ma)001:1676: kyang / rtagsa dang k+ai la ya'i srid pa'i dabnga
NK016(ma)001:1677: dang khams gsum gyis bdag mo mthu'i dbang phyug ma
NK016(ma)001:1678: badga nyid chen mo gshegsa su gsola /
NK016(ma)001:1679: de lta bu'i ma mo'i tshogs nad kyis bdag mo re ma ti mched bzhi gshegsa nasa kyang /
NK016(ma)001:1680: rtags dang k+ai la ya'i khyod kyis dam tshig dus la baba ces pa /
NK016(ma)001:1681: phur pa'i srung ma ma lus pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1682: mthu rtsal phyungs ces pa dam can bcu gnyis kyi 'khor na /
NK016(ma)001:1683: bdud ni rol chen la sogs pa'i dregs pa pho
NK016(ma)001:1684: bdud nyi shu rtsa gcig 'khor yang 'khor dang bcas
NK016(ma)001:1685: pa rnams kyis sems kyis mthu dang /
NK016(ma)001:1686: lus kyis rtsal phyung ba'i phyir gshegas su gsola /
NK016(ma)001:1687: de lta bu'i dregsa pa nyi shu rtsa gciga gshegsa nasa kyang /
NK016(ma)001:1688: rtagsa dang k+ai la ya'i dngosa grub stsol /
NK016(ma)001:1690: khyed kyis dam tshig dus la bab //
NK016(ma)001:1691: mthu rtsal phyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK016(ma)001:1694: gdul byed spyi la thams cad gnan nas bskul ba ste /
NK016(ma)001:1695: dang po ye shes pa ltar na /
NK016(ma)001:1696: khyed de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis dam tshig ni /
NK016(ma)001:1697: thugs rjes 'gro ba sgrol ba yin pas de'i dus la bab pas /
NK016(ma)001:1698: sems kyis mthu dang lus kyis rgyu rtsal dang /
NK016(ma)001:1699: sprul pa bsam gyis mi khyab pas 'gro ba'i don gyis shig pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1701: dam can dang dregs pa khyed rnams kyis dam tshig ni /
NK016(ma)001:1702: sngon bcom ldan 'das sh+r+ai badz+ra ku ma ra'i spyan
NK016(ma)001:1703: sngar srog gis snying po mdong sol du phul ste
NK016(ma)001:1704: / ma 'ongs pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams kyis grogs bya ba dang /
NK016(ma)001:1705: dgra bgegs gdug pa can bsgral bar dam bca' ba yin pas /
NK016(ma)001:1706: de'i dus deng sang yin ces pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1707: de yang khyed rnams kyis sems kyis mthu dang /
NK016(ma)001:1708: lus kyis sprul pa'i sgyu rtsal cir yang mnga' bas
NK016(ma)001:1709: dpyad sgrub po la sdong grogs mdzod ces pa dang
NK016(ma)001:1710: / dgra bgegs gdug pa can bsgral ba'i dus la deng sang bab bo //
NK016(ma)001:1712: de ltar bskyed pa'i da la 'dra ba gcig byon nas /
NK016(ma)001:1713: gtso bo la gtso bo dang /
NK016(ma)001:1715: gzhal yang khang la gzhal yas khang /
NK016(ma)001:1716: rdo rwa me ri la rdo rwa me ri rnams thim par bsam mo //
NK016(ma)001:1717: bdun pa dbang bskur ba ni /
NK016(ma)001:1718: yangs man dzas snyan gsan dbab la /
NK016(ma)001:1719: rang gis thugs ka'i 'od zer gyis phyogs bcu'i b+hud+d+ha
NK016(ma)001:1720: thams cad bsdus te kun kyang rdo rje gzhon nu
NK016(ma)001:1721: rang 'dra bas nam mkha' gang bar bzhugs par bsgom
NK016(ma)001:1722: la / de nas thugs yang dag pa'i ye shes skye 'jig dang bral bas rdo rje /
NK016(ma)001:1723: de nyid bgres rgud dang bral bas gzhona nu /
NK016(ma)001:1724: de'i rig ni chos sku ste /
NK016(ma)001:1725: dus gsum gyis sangs rgyas thams cad kyis de nyid rtogs pa na 'dzina pa ste /
NK016(ma)001:1727: yang phyogs bcu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor /
NK016(ma)001:1729: khra thabs kyis kyang chos sku'i don rtogs pas rig 'dzin ces bya ste /
NK016(ma)001:1732: mi srid pa'i srid pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:1733: ji srid pa'i srid pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:1735: mi srid pa'i srid pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:1736: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la bya ste /
NK016(ma)001:1737: sangs rgyas ni rgya lam na lan gcig srid pa sa mi srid ba zhes bya ste /
NK016(ma)001:1738: de yang dpal rdo rje gzhon nu'i thugs kyi rang bzhin yin pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:1739: ji srid pa'i srid pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:1740: byang chub sems dpa' dang nyan rang la bya ste /
NK016(ma)001:1741: de yang rgya lam lan gcig na srid la /
NK016(ma)001:1742: ji srid pa'i srid pa zhes bya ste /
NK016(ma)001:1743: de yang rdo rje gzhon nu'i gsung gis rang bzhin yin pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:1745: lha mi ngan song kun la bya ste /
NK016(ma)001:1746: de yang rdo rje gzhon nu'i sku'i rang bzhin yin pas srid pa gsum dang /
NK016(ma)001:1747: yang na srid pa lha mi ngan song gsum mo //
NK016(ma)001:1755: yang na srid pa khams gsum mo //
NK016(ma)001:1756: yang na srid pa lus ngag yid gsum ste /
NK016(ma)001:1757: de ltar srid pa bco brgyad po kun rdo rje
NK016(ma)001:1758: gzhon nu'i sku gsung thugs su dbyer mi phyed pas
NK016(ma)001:1759: rdo rje ste / de lta bu'i ngang du grub par mdzoda ciga ces pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1760: de ltar srid pa kun rdo rje gzhon nu'i sku
NK016(ma)001:1761: gsung thugs rdo rje bdag nyid du gyur pas na
NK016(ma)001:1762: / thams cad rdo rje gzhon nu'i srung ma'am phur pa'i lhar ma gyur pa med pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1764: de nyid rtogs pa'i rig pa gnyis su med pa
NK016(ma)001:1765: de la ye shesa khro bo zhes pa ye shes
NK016(ma)001:1766: chen po sngon du btang bas khro ba ltar bcas
NK016(ma)001:1767: pa dang / thugs rje chen po'i shugs kyis khro ba ltar bcas pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1768: de lta bu'i sku de rnal 'byor pa bdag la grub par mdzod cig pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1769: spangs rtogs phun sum tshogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyis
NK016(ma)001:1770: rtogs pa'i ye shes sku lnga dbyer med pa'i ngang
NK016(ma)001:1771: nyid rdo rje chos kyis dbyingsa lasa /
NK016(ma)001:1772: thugs ye shes rtogs pa 'abra ba dang /
NK016(ma)001:1773: thugs rje chen po'i phrin las 'bar ba dang /
NK016(ma)001:1774: khrag 'thung chen po'i sku mtshan dang dpe byad kyis 'bar ba'i khro bo ni 'bru mthun la /
NK016(ma)001:1775: mi bazada pa ces pa gdul bya 'dul ba'i dbang
NK016(ma)001:1776: du 'jig rten pa dang mthun par khro bo rngam
NK016(ma)001:1778: yang na mi bzad pa ste /
NK016(ma)001:1779: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las gdul bya ci tsam du yod pa de tsam du snang ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:1780: de lta bu'i sku'i dbyig gam ngo ba nyid du
NK016(ma)001:1781: badga rnal 'byor ba gyur cig pa'am bskyed ciga pa'o
NK016(ma)001:1782: // sangsa rgyas kun gyi ye shes gsunga gis nganga nyid rdo rje chosa kyi dbyingsa lasa /
NK016(ma)001:1783: 'abra ba'i khro bo mi bazada pa /
NK016(ma)001:1784: gsunga gisa dbyig gam ngo bo nyid du badga rnal 'byor pa gyur cig pa'am bskyed cig pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1785: sangsa rgyas kun gyis ye shes thugsa /
NK016(ma)001:1786: badga nyid rdo rje chosa dbyingsa las /
NK016(ma)001:1787: 'abra ba'i khro bo mi bazada pa /
NK016(ma)001:1788: thugsa kyi dbyig gam ngo bo nyid du badga rnal 'byor pa gyur cig pa'am /
NK016(ma)001:1791: gdul bya 'dul ba'i thabas kyi mdzad spyod sna tshogs pasa 'gro ba 'dul ba'i dona du /
NK016(ma)001:1792: de'i rgyu byamsa pa dang snying rje'am /
NK016(ma)001:1793: thugs rje ganga la gang 'dula de la der ston
NK016(ma)001:1794: pa'i sangas rgyas kyis che ba'i yon tan thams cad
NK016(ma)001:1795: bdag rnal 'byor pa la rdzogas par madzada nasa /
NK016(ma)001:1796: rang rig lhun grub kyis dbang dang /
NK016(ma)001:1797: khams gsum dbang du sdud pa'i dabnga dang /
NK016(ma)001:1798: gdug pa za byed kyis dbang dang byin rlabs thams cad badga la stsol cig pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1799: thabsa byams dang snying rje sangsa rgyas kyi phrin lasa
NK016(ma)001:1800: zhi rgyas dbang drag lhun grub rnams rdzogsa par madzada
NK016(ma)001:1801: nas / dabnga dang byin rlabsa badga la stsol ciga pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1802: de ltar du gsol ba btab pa ste /
NK016(ma)001:1803: de yang rdo rje gzhon nu'i rig 'dzin rnams ces
NK016(ma)001:1804: pa'i shwa lo ka dang po spyir bstan pa yin
NK016(ma)001:1805: la / 'og ma lnga ni bye brag tu gsol ba btab pa yin te /
NK016(ma)001:1806: de ltar du gsol ba btab pa'i sku gsung thugs
NK016(ma)001:1807: yon tan phrin las lnga'i dngos grub thob par bsam
NK016(ma)001:1808: pa ni / mdun gyi lha de dag gis thugs
NK016(ma)001:1809: ka nas dkar po byung nas bdag gis spyi bor
NK016(ma)001:1810: pa ni / thim pas / sku'i dbang thob par bsam /
NK016(ma)001:1811: da lta nas lus kyi g.yo 'gul ci byas kyang
NK016(ma)001:1812: 'gro ba sgrol ba'i nus pa dang ldan par bsam
NK016(ma)001:1813: / sangs rgyas pa'i dus su mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK016(ma)001:1814: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu'i dbang thob par bsam /
NK016(ma)001:1816: +aahdamara po bdag gis mgrin par thim pas /
NK016(ma)001:1817: gsung gis dbang thob par bsam /
NK016(ma)001:1818: da ltar gyis ngag bzlas brjod ci byas kyang /
NK016(ma)001:1819: 'gro ba sgrol ba'i nus pa dang ldan par bsam /
NK016(ma)001:1820: sangs rgyas pa'i dus su gsung dbyangs yan lag sum brgya drug cu la dbang thob par bsam /
NK016(ma)001:1822: h'u mthing nag bdag gis thugs kar thim /
NK016(ma)001:1823: thugs kyi dbang thob par bsam /
NK016(ma)001:1824: da lta nas ting nge 'dzin ci ltar na yang
NK016(ma)001:1825: 'gro ba sgrol ba'i nus pa dang ldan par bsam
NK016(ma)001:1826: / sangs rgyas pa'i dus su ting nge 'dzin sgo 'bum phrag du ma la dbang thob par bsam /
NK016(ma)001:1828: ces s+w+aa ser po byung bas bdag gis lte bar thim yon tan gyi dbang thob par bsam /
NK016(ma)001:1829: de ltar nas tshe ring nad med bkra shis longs spyod 'phel ba la sogs pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1830: b+hud+d+ha'i dus na bde bar gshegs pa'i yon tan brgya bzhi bcu la mnga' brnyes pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1832: h+aa ljang ku byung bas bdag gis gsang gnas su thim phrin las kyi dbang thob par bsam /
NK016(ma)001:1833: da lta nas phrin las rnam bzhi lhun gyi grub pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1834: sangs rgyas pa'i dus su bde bar gshegs pa'i thugs
NK016(ma)001:1835: rje'i phrin las thams cad la mnga' brnyes par bsam
NK016(ma)001:1836: / de nas rdo rje gzhon nu'i lha tshogs de rnams bdag la bstim mo //
NK016(ma)001:1837: yang na rdo rje gzhon nu'i rig 'dzin rnams //
NK016(ma)001:1839: yar gsol ba btab pa yin la /
NK016(ma)001:1840: 'og ma lnga ni de'i lan du gsung par bsam la dngos grub blang /
NK016(ma)001:1841: ces bla ma gong ma rnams kyi gsungs so //
NK016(ma)001:1842: spyi don brgyad pa mchod pa 'bul ba ni /
NK016(ma)001:1843: rnam lnga yid kyi lha mo rnams kyis /
NK016(ma)001:1844: yon chab ni lha tshogs rnams kyi zhal dang zhabs bsil /
NK016(ma)001:1848: dri chab lus la byug go //
NK016(ma)001:1852: sngags kyis rak+ta gsal gdab la /
NK016(ma)001:1854: dam tshiga chen po'i dus la baba /
NK016(ma)001:1855: ces pa la sogs pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:1857: 'dod chags ma spangs gnas su dag par bya ba'i phyir du /
NK016(ma)001:1858: rak+ta damra gyis mchoda pa bzhes su gsol /
NK016(ma)001:1860: mthu rtsal phyung rak+ta lha tshogs rnams rang rang gis sngags kyis mthar kh+aa hi btags la /
NK016(ma)001:1861: lha mo thod zhal thogs pa rnams kyi bcus nas mchod par bsam mo //
NK016(ma)001:1865: dam tshiga chena po'i dus la bab /
NK016(ma)001:1866: gti mug ma spangs gnas su dag par bya ba'i phyir du /
NK016(ma)001:1867: b+ha linga rgyan gyi gtor ma bzhesa su gsol //
NK016(ma)001:1869: mthu rtsal b+ha ling lha tshogs rnams kyi rang rang gis sngags kyis mthar kh+aa hi btags la /
NK016(ma)001:1872: mchod pa'i lha mo rnams kyi rin po che'i skyog bsnams nas /
NK016(ma)001:1873: lha tshogs rnams la drang bar bsam /
NK016(ma)001:1874: 'og dug gsum sha khrag rus pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:1875: khyad par du khro bo'i lha tshogs dang chos skyong rnams la mchod par bsam /
NK016(ma)001:1876: de nas sman gyi mchod pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:1879: ho ranga byung gdoda nasa dag pa yi /
NK016(ma)001:1882: dam tshiga chen po'i dus la baba /
NK016(ma)001:1883: bcoma ldan dapala chen rdo rje gzhona nu yaba yum la /
NK016(ma)001:1884: zhe sdang ma spangs gnas su dag par bya ba'i phyir du /
NK016(ma)001:1885: rnam daga thugsa rjesa mgo 'dren na ma phyag 'tshal /
NK016(ma)001:1887: ta th+aa ga ta de bzhin gshegs pa /
NK016(ma)001:1889: ar+g+ham mchod yon pra ti dza ho so sor mnyes pa ste /
NK016(ma)001:1890: don du na de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad mchod
NK016(ma)001:1891: yon chen po bdud rtsi sman gyi so sor mnyes
NK016(ma)001:1893: de'i dus su lha mo nyi zla'i skyog thogs pa dpag tu med pa byung nas mchod par bsam /
NK016(ma)001:1894: de nas yi dam spyi la kh+aa hi btag go //
NK016(ma)001:1895: spyi don dgu pa bstod pa bya ba ni /
NK016(ma)001:1896: 'khor rnams kyi gtso bo la bstod par bsam la /
NK016(ma)001:1902: yon tan la bstod pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:1903: phrin las la bstod pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:1904: khro bo spyi la bstod pa'am /
NK016(ma)001:1905: dbang chen gyis dkyil 'khor la bstod pa dang drug go //
NK016(ma)001:1906: 'di'i don zhib bar gsang snying le'u nyer gcig pa'i nang du zhib par yod pas der gzigs mdzod /
NK016(ma)001:1907: de nas bsnyen pa'i gong la phreng ba byin rlabs bya ste /
NK016(ma)001:1909: zhi rgyas dbang drag bzhi'i phreng ba'i kha dog dang /
NK016(ma)001:1911: 'dren pa'i thabs rnams gzhan du shes par bya'o //
NK016(ma)001:1912: bcu pa bsnyen pa bya ba la bzhi ste /
NK016(ma)001:1913: k+ai la ya rgyud kyis bsnyen pa dang gcig /
NK016(ma)001:1914: lung gi bsnyen pa dang gnyis /
NK016(ma)001:1915: man ngag gi bsnyen pa dang gsum /
NK016(ma)001:1916: ngan sngags kyi bsnyen pa dang bzhi'o //
NK016(ma)001:1917: de la rgyud kyi bsnyen pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:1918: bdag rdo rje gzhon nu'i thugs ka nas nyi ma'i
NK016(ma)001:1919: dkyil 'khor gyis steng du ye shes sems dpa' rang
NK016(ma)001:1921: de'i thugs kar nyi ma'i steng du rdo rje nag po rtse dgu pa yar bzhengs pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1922: de'i lte ba khong seng stongs par nyi ma'i steng du h'u mthing nag yar bzhengs pa /
NK016(ma)001:1924: badz+ra k+ai li k+aa la ya h'u phata ces pas /
NK016(ma)001:1925: yi ge mthing nag yar bzhengs pa g.yas su 'khor ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:1926: khro bo rnams kyi thugs ka na yang nyi ma'i steng du /
NK016(ma)001:1927: rdo rje nag po khong stongs rtse lnga re re yar bzhengs pa /
NK016(ma)001:1928: de'i lte ba'i nang du nyi ma'i steng du h'u mthing nag re re la /
NK016(ma)001:1929: de la khro bo rang rang gis sngags kyi bskor ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:1930: dam can bcu gnyis kyi bswe mo bzhi'i spyi bor /
NK016(ma)001:1931: glad pa dung khang gis nang du sa'i dkyil 'khor
NK016(ma)001:1932: gru bzhi ser po re re'i steng du dkar po
NK016(ma)001:1934: de la bdud kyis bu mo'i spyi bor ma tha ma tha badz+ra ces pas 'khor ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:1935: lho sgor gaza'i bu mo'i spyir bor dz+wa la dz+wa la badz+ra ces pas 'khor ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:1936: nub sgor btsan gyis bu mo'i spyi bor su ru su ru badz+ra ces pas 'khor ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:1937: byang sgor klu'i bu mo'i spyi bor mu ru mu ru badz+ra ces 'khor ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:1938: de ni bswe mo bzhi'i yi ge dang /
NK016(ma)001:1939: srog snying bsgom pa'i rim pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1940: shwa na bzhi'i mgrin par rlung gi dal dud ka
NK016(ma)001:1941: zla gam du 'dug pa'i dkyil du +aahdamara po re
NK016(ma)001:1942: re bsgom / lcags kyi spyang mo mgo dgu ma'i
NK016(ma)001:1943: mgrin par ha na ha na badz+ra ces pas 'khor
NK016(ma)001:1944: re bsgom / ba'o // lcags kyi khyi mo rkang
NK016(ma)001:1945: gsum la zhon pa'i bud med nag mo'i mgrin par
NK016(ma)001:1946: da ha da ha badz+ra ces pas 'khor ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:1947: zangs kyi 'phar ba lce brgyad kyis mgrin par pa tsa pa tsa badz+ra ces /
NK016(ma)001:1948: zangs kyi wa mo rkang gsum la zhon pa'i bud
NK016(ma)001:1949: med kyis mgrin par ma tha ma tha badz+ra ces
NK016(ma)001:1950: / de ni shwa na bzhi'i srog snying dgod pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1951: re ma ti bzhi'i thugs kar me'i dal 'khor lo
NK016(ma)001:1952: dmar nag gru gsum pa re re'i steng du h'u
NK016(ma)001:1953: mthing nag re re bsgom mo //
NK016(ma)001:1955: h'u ma ma pa sham ku ru ma stam dz+ny+aa
NK016(ma)001:1956: na ka ra ye nan d+ha ti ma ma karma
NK016(ma)001:1957: sh+ri kram ka ra ya h'u phata ces pas 'khor
NK016(ma)001:1958: ba'o // de nas dmigs pa gsal gdab /
NK016(ma)001:1960: ngag mtshams bcad nas thugs ka'i ye shes sems dpa' dang /
NK016(ma)001:1961: rdo rje'i lte ba'i h'u dang /
NK016(ma)001:1962: yi ge g.yas su 'khor ba'i gu gu dang /
NK016(ma)001:1964: zhabs kyu la ma yengs par zur phyin par byas la yid sems gtad /
NK016(ma)001:1965: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata ces bzlas pas /
NK016(ma)001:1966: rang gis thugs ka nas yi ge'i phreng ba la yi ge'i phreng ba gcig chad nas /
NK016(ma)001:1967: mgrin pa nas ljags kyis rtse mo nas thon /
NK016(ma)001:1969: phyogs bcu'i b+hud+d+ha thams cad kyang dpal rdo rje gzhon
NK016(ma)001:1970: nu'i cha lugs su byung nas nam mkha' la 'khrigs
NK016(ma)001:1971: / rang gis sngags bzlas pa tsam gyis /
NK016(ma)001:1972: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyis kyang bdag gis ram bu'i tshul du bzlas te /
NK016(ma)001:1973: k+ai la ya 'bru dgu las 'phel te /
NK016(ma)001:1974: k+ai la ya'i sgra 'u ru ru sgrogs par bsam /
NK016(ma)001:1975: sngags kyis sgra las 'od zer byung bas /
NK016(ma)001:1981: bdag dang sangs rgyas thams cad kyis 'od zer yin te /
NK016(ma)001:1982: sems can thams cad kyis lus ngag yid gsum gyis sgrib pa sbyangs te /
NK016(ma)001:1983: slar sems can thams cad rdo rje gzhon nur gyur par bsam /
NK016(ma)001:1985: 'od zer dang yig 'bru rnams bdag la bstim pas /

NK016(ma)001:1987: phra mo them gang nem gang dpag tu med pas

NK016(ma)001:1990: phyogs bcu'i b+hud+d+ha rdo rje gzhon nu'i skur gyur pa rnams ni bdag gis thugs kar bstim /
NK016(ma)001:1992: sman raka gtor gsum byin gyis brlabs la 'bul /
NK016(ma)001:1993: de ni k+ai la ya 'bru dgu'i bsnyen pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:1994: k+ai la la 'bru bcu bzhi'i bsnyen pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:1995: khro bo bcu sbrel mar bya ste /
NK016(ma)001:1996: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba b+hig+nana bam h'u phata /
NK016(ma)001:1997: badz+ra kro d+ha h'u ka ra h'u gardza gardza h'u phata /
NK016(ma)001:1998: badz+ra kro d+ha bi dza ya h'u /
NK016(ma)001:1999: ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK016(ma)001:2000: badz+ra kro d+ha ni la dan+da h'u /
NK016(ma)001:2001: da ha da ha h'u phata /
NK016(ma)001:2002: badz+ra kro d+ha ya m+aan+ta ka h'u /
NK016(ma)001:2003: pa tsa pa tsa h'u phata /
NK016(ma)001:2004: badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h'u /
NK016(ma)001:2006: badz+ra kro d+ha h+ya g+r+ai ba h'u /
NK016(ma)001:2007: hu lu hu lu h'u phata /

NK016(ma)001:2010: badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da li h'u /
NK016(ma)001:2012: badz+ra tree lo kya bi dza ya h'u /
NK016(ma)001:2014: badz+ra kro d+ha ma h+aa ba la h'u /
NK016(ma)001:2015: s+pho ta s+pho ta h'u phata /
NK016(ma)001:2016: k+ai la ya 'bru bcu bzhi bas mgo drangs /
NK016(ma)001:2017: khro bcu'i sngags dang bcas pa rang gis dag tu bzlas pas /
NK016(ma)001:2018: rang gi thugs ka nas k+ai la ya g.yas su 'khor ba las /
NK016(ma)001:2020: gzhal yas khang gis nam mkha' la 'khrigs te /
NK016(ma)001:2021: phyogs bcu'i khro bo khra thabs rnams kyang rang sngags brjod par bsam zhing /
NK016(ma)001:2022: rang gis thugs kar yang rang sngags 'khor te /
NK016(ma)001:2024: bdag rdo rje gzhon nu'i 'od zer dang gnyis po des /
NK016(ma)001:2025: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyis sku gsung thugs kyis rgyud bskul /
NK016(ma)001:2026: sems can thams cad kyis lus ngag yid gsum gyi sgrib pa sbyangs te /
NK016(ma)001:2027: slar 'od zer thams cad la khro bo 'chol ba'i tshogs kyis /
NK016(ma)001:2028: chos kyi dbyings kyi mtha' klas pa'i b+hud+d+ha'i zhing khams
NK016(ma)001:2029: la thugs kyis bar du khro bo 'chol ba'i tshogs
NK016(ma)001:2030: kyis bkang nas / bdud dang mu stegs ma h+aa de b+aa dang /
NK016(ma)001:2031: tshangs pa khyab 'jug rnams tshar bcad nas /
NK016(ma)001:2032: sangs rgyas thams cad ni re zhig dam pa'i tshul du dgongs /
NK016(ma)001:2033: ma mo dang mkha' 'gro thams cad ni dpa' bskyed /
NK016(ma)001:2034: byang chub sems dpa' rnams ni thugs mnyam pa nyid las bzhengs /
NK016(ma)001:2035: nyan thos rang rgyal rnams ni 'gog pa'i mtha' las bslangs /
NK016(ma)001:2036: dgra bgegs gdug pa can rnams tshar bcad /
NK016(ma)001:2037: khams gsum gyis sems can thams cad kyis log rtog zil gyis mnan ste /
NK016(ma)001:2038: khro bo rnams kyis sngags kyi sgra yang dper na bskal pa'i 'brug stong ldir ba'am /
NK016(ma)001:2040: gnam lcags thog gis sgra lta bu stong gsum dbang du sdud pa'am /
NK016(ma)001:2041: srid gsum zil gyis gnon pa'i tshul du bzlas pa bya'o //
NK016(ma)001:2042: nam 'jog pa'i dus su 'od zer thams cad bdag gis thugs kar bstim /
NK016(ma)001:2044: de ni phyogs bcu'i khro ba dang khra thabs kyis bsnyen pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:2045: dam can gyis bsnyen pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:2046: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata /
NK016(ma)001:2050: mu ru mu ru badz+ra ces brjod pas rang gis
NK016(ma)001:2051: thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros bas bswe mo bzhi
NK016(ma)001:2052: la phog / bswe mo bzhi'i sngags g.yas su 'khor ba dang /
NK016(ma)001:2053: sa bon las 'od zer 'phros pas bswe mo bzhi'i rang gnas bzhi ste /
NK016(ma)001:2058: bswe mo nyis brgya lnga bcu /
NK016(ma)001:2059: rang gis thugs dam gyis rgyud bskul nas /
NK016(ma)001:2060: grong rgyug gi bswe mo yan chad kyis mkha' 'gro
NK016(ma)001:2061: ma gdug pa can thams cad kyis srog snying de
NK016(ma)001:2063: bswe mo bzhi yang sngar bas bkrag gzi mdangs dang ldan /
NK016(ma)001:2064: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul dang ldan pa /
NK016(ma)001:2065: slar srog gis snying po bdag la mdangs sol du phul nas /
NK016(ma)001:2066: bdag gis thugs ka'i h'u gis zhabs kyu'i bar du thim par bsam /
NK016(ma)001:2067: tshar nas stong tshig gis mchod pa 'bul /
NK016(ma)001:2068: shwa na bzhi'i bsnyen pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:2069: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata /
NK016(ma)001:2074: shwa na bzhi'i sngags brjod pa tsam gyis /
NK016(ma)001:2075: rang gi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros te /
NK016(ma)001:2076: shwa na bzhi'i mgrin par phog /
NK016(ma)001:2079: shwa na sum brgya drug cu dang /
NK016(ma)001:2080: ye shes dang 'jig rten pa'i chos skyong thams cad kyis thugs kar phog thugs dam gyis rgyud bskul /
NK016(ma)001:2081: srog gi snying po shwa na bzhi'i thugs kar bstim /

NK016(ma)001:2083: 'jog khar shwa na bzhi'i srog gis snying po a

NK016(ma)001:2087: re ma ti bzhi'i bsnyen pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:2088: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata /
NK016(ma)001:2089: ma ma ba sham ku ru ma stam dz+ny+aa na

NK016(ma)001:2093: re ma ti bzhi'i srog gi snying po sa bon dang bcas la phog /
NK016(ma)001:2096: ma mo dang mkha' 'gro ma dus bzhi'i rgyal mo
NK016(ma)001:2097: srid pa gsum gyi ma tshogs dang bcas pa'i thugs
NK016(ma)001:2098: kar phog / thugs dam gyis rgyud bskul nas /
NK016(ma)001:2099: re ma ti'i thugs kar bstim /
NK016(ma)001:2100: sngar bas kyang bkrag gzi mdangs dang ldan par bsam nas /

NK016(ma)001:2104: dregs byed nyi shu rtsa gcig la thugs kar srog snying 'bul ba med de /
NK016(ma)001:2105: ma ra sa na ye h'u phata /
NK016(ma)001:2106: bra ma ta na ye h'u phata /
NK016(ma)001:2107: a bi ta na ye h'u phata /
NK016(ma)001:2108: dza ye bi dza ye h'u phata /
NK016(ma)001:2109: a pa ra dzi ta h'u phata /
NK016(ma)001:2110: dam can gyis rting par brgya re tsam bzlas pas /

NK016(ma)001:2112: ba'i las byed cing bcol pa'i phrin las bsgrub par
NK016(ma)001:2113: bsam mo // k+ai la ya rgyud ma h+aa yo ga ltar bsnyen pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:2114: k+ai la ya lung gis bsnyen pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:2116: snang srid 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad rang rig pa'i ngo bo /
NK016(ma)001:2117: rang byung gis yi shes gsal la sgrib pa med pa /
NK016(ma)001:2118: skye 'gag med pa'i dbyings ngang gis ma bcos pa /
NK016(ma)001:2119: snga phyi thog mtha' dang bral ba /
NK016(ma)001:2120: ngang gis 'od gsal la sgrib pa med pa /
NK016(ma)001:2121: rgya mtsho chen po'i gting mi g.yo ba lta bu /
NK016(ma)001:2122: de'i ngang la rdo rje gzhon nu'i lha tshogs thams cad rang rig rang snang ste /
NK016(ma)001:2123: gsal la go mi 'gags pa rgya mtsho'i nang gis gzugs brnyan lta bu'o //
NK016(ma)001:2124: de nas rdo rje gzhon nu'i snying pos mgo drangs ste /
NK016(ma)001:2125: khro bo khra thabs dang bcas pa /
NK016(ma)001:2126: dam can dang bcas pa'i sngags bzlas pas /
NK016(ma)001:2127: dal gyis lha tshogs rnams kyi kyang rang gis ram
NK016(ma)001:2128: bu'i tshul du rang rang gis sngags rang rang gis
NK016(ma)001:2131: rlung sgra thams cad kyang rnams kyis sgrar bsam te /
NK016(ma)001:2132: sems ma bcos pa'i ngang la /
NK016(ma)001:2133: dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs thams cad chu nang gis gzugs brnyan ltar rig pa rang gsal rang snang /
NK016(ma)001:2136: sngags kyis 'od zer yang kha dog sna lnga'i tshul du gzhal yas khang du rang snang ste /
NK016(ma)001:2138: rigs lnga'i 'khor lo'i tshogs su gyur nas rang gis thugs kar bstim /
NK016(ma)001:2139: de yang a nu yo ga'i blo dang ldan pa zhig gis lag len yin ste /
NK016(ma)001:2140: gar thod thod du ma yin no //
NK016(ma)001:2141: spyir lung gis bzlas pa 'di la sems kyis ngo bo stong ste ma bcos par 'jog /
NK016(ma)001:2142: sems kyis rang bzhin 'od gsal te /
NK016(ma)001:2143: dal gyis lha tshogs stong pa'i ngang la me long gis gzugs brnyan ltar bkra lam gyi gsal /
NK016(ma)001:2145: lha tshogs thams cad kyang snang bzhin du stong /
NK016(ma)001:2147: de'i ngang la sngags thams cad dus gcig tu bzlas pas /
NK016(ma)001:2148: stong nyid kyis ngang du sgra rang grags /
NK016(ma)001:2149: grags tsam nyid na brag cha bzhin du rang bzhin
NK016(ma)001:2150: med pa'i ngang las lha dang sngags kyis sgra rang
NK016(ma)001:2151: snang / snang dus stong nas kyang yid la mi byed par ma bcos pa'i ngang la rang bzhag /
NK016(ma)001:2152: de la ma skyes pa stong pa ni dbyings /
NK016(ma)001:2153: ma 'gags pa sgra thams cad sngags kyi sgrar grags pa ni rig pa'i ye shes so //
NK016(ma)001:2154: gnyis su med pa ma 'gags par ma bcos pa
NK016(ma)001:2155: rang bzhag pa ni gnyis med bde ba chen po'o
NK016(ma)001:2156: // tshar nas stong tshig gis mchod pa rnam lnga 'bul /
NK016(ma)001:2157: lung +aa nu yo ga rang gzhung gis bsnyen pa'o //
NK016(ma)001:2158: man ngag gis bsnyen pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:2159: chos rdzogs pa chen po dang tshul mthun te /
NK016(ma)001:2160: dbang bzhi'i don la ngo 'phrod pa'am /
NK016(ma)001:2161: chos rdzogs pa chen po'i don khong du chud pa zhig gis /
NK016(ma)001:2162: chos thams cad kyis brjod bya /
NK016(ma)001:2163: theg pa thams cad kyis yang rtse /
NK016(ma)001:2164: man ngag thams cad kyis snying khu /
NK016(ma)001:2165: bla ma brgyud pa'i nyams su myong ba'i don gcig tu dril ste /
NK016(ma)001:2166: rang rig pa 'di b+hud+d+ha thams cad kyis de kho na nyid yin pas /

NK016(ma)001:2168: dmigs gtad med pa'i bsgom pa yang 'di /
NK016(ma)001:2169: bya btsal med pa'i spyod pa yang 'di /
NK016(ma)001:2170: spang thob med pa'i 'bras bu yang 'di /
NK016(ma)001:2171: yid la mi byed pa dus gsum rang gsal chen po yang yin /
NK016(ma)001:2172: brgyad khri bzhi stong chos kyi brjod bya yin /
NK016(ma)001:2173: rang byung dang du rang lugs chen por bzhag /

NK016(ma)001:2183: bya rgyu rdul tsam ma mchis so //

NK016(ma)001:2193: a we sha ya a we sha ya h'u phat+aa
NK016(ma)001:2194: dz+wa la pa ya dz+wa la pa ya h'u phata
NK016(ma)001:2195: / ta th+aa ya ta th+aa ya h'u phata /
NK016(ma)001:2196: b+han+d+ha ya b+han+d+ha ya h'u phata /
NK016(ma)001:2197: ma ra sa na pra mar+d+ha na ye h'u phata /
NK016(ma)001:2198: sarba a na ya h'u phata /
NK016(ma)001:2199: h'u h'u ma ma pa sham ku ru ma stam
NK016(ma)001:2200: dz+ny+aa na ka ra e nan d+ha ti ma ma
NK016(ma)001:2201: karma sh+ri kram ka ra ya h'u phata /
NK016(ma)001:2202: lam h'u lam stam+b+ha ya nan /
NK016(ma)001:2203: mo h+aa g+h+aa ya b+ha ga wan h+r+aish+ti n+ri we kri badz+ra h'u k+aa ra h'u h'u phata phata /
NK016(ma)001:2204: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dza h'u bam ho /
NK016(ma)001:2205: sarba b+hig+nana badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u h'u h'u phata phata phata /
NK016(ma)001:2208: de ltar bzlas pas srung ma gsum gyi srog gis gnad thams cad ngo bo ni /
NK016(ma)001:2210: rten gyis spyi bo nas dbyibs zlum po kha dog dkar po srog gis snying po 'khor ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:2212: mgrin par zla gam dmar po steng a dmar po la srog gis snying pos bskor ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:2214: snying kha nas gru gsum lam bring nag ste /
NK016(ma)001:2215: de la srog gis snying po 'khor ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:2217: srung ma'i srog gis ngo bo dang /
NK016(ma)001:2220: snying po shin tu gsal bar gyur par bsam mo //
NK016(ma)001:2221: dper na spra ba la me 'bar ba la /
NK016(ma)001:2222: rlung gis btab pas shin tu gsal ba dang 'dra'o //
NK016(ma)001:2223: de la srung ma bred nas dpal chen po la ci bgyis bka' nyan zer bar bsam mo //
NK016(ma)001:2225: de ltar bsnyen pa byas pas rtags 'byung ste /
NK016(ma)001:2226: grub pa'i drod tshad ni rnam pa gsum ste /
NK016(ma)001:2230: de la dbye na rab 'bring dgu ste /
NK016(ma)001:2231: rab kyi rab kyis rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum zhal mthong /
NK016(ma)001:2232: rab kyi 'bring gis rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum nyams ltas su 'ong /
NK016(ma)001:2233: rab kyi tha mas rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum rmi ltas su 'ong ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:2234: 'bring gi rab kyis khro bo yab yum bcu zhal mthong /
NK016(ma)001:2235: 'bring gi 'bring gis khro bo yum bcu nyams ltas su 'ong /
NK016(ma)001:2236: 'bring gi tha mas rmi ltas su 'ong /
NK016(ma)001:2237: tha ma'i rab kyis khra thabs nyi shu zhal mthong /
NK016(ma)001:2238: tha ma'i 'bring gis nyams ltas su 'ong /
NK016(ma)001:2239: tha ma'i tha mas rmi ltas su 'ong /
NK016(ma)001:2240: de dag gang byung yang tshogs bya zhing /
NK016(ma)001:2241: khams gsum yang sgrol gyis dngos grub kyang blang ngo //
NK016(ma)001:2242: de la lus rdul du bsdu zhing dgra bgegs thal
NK016(ma)001:2243: ba rdul du brlag pa'i phrin las la 'jug par
NK016(ma)001:2244: bya'o // phrin las grub pa'i rtags ni /
NK016(ma)001:2245: don bcu gnyis kyi grub rtags 'byung ba ni /
NK016(ma)001:2246: sku'i rigs grub pa'i rtags ni /
NK016(ma)001:2247: bswe mo mched bzhi mngon du mthong ba dang /
NK016(ma)001:2250: thugs kyi grub rtags 'byung ba ni /
NK016(ma)001:2251: re ma ti bzhi'i zhal mthong ba dang /
NK016(ma)001:2255: shwa na bzhi'i zhal mthong ba dang /
NK016(ma)001:2257: rmi ltas su rmi ba dang gsum mo //
NK016(ma)001:2258: de dag kyang zhal mthong ba rab kyis drod tshad /
NK016(ma)001:2260: rmi ltas ni tha ma'i grub rtags so //
NK016(ma)001:2261: de dag kyang gang byung na yang /
NK016(ma)001:2262: gdug pa can dbang du bsdu ba /
NK016(ma)001:2263: dgra bgegs bsgral ba'i phrin las bya /
NK016(ma)001:2264: bsgral ba'i las la dbang ba'i dngos grub blang /
NK016(ma)001:2266: dam can rnams rang gis thugs kar bsdu ba'o //
NK016(ma)001:2267: lar phur pa bsgrub pa'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK016(ma)001:2268: gsang sngags phyi'i dam tshig nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyang dang du blang /
NK016(ma)001:2269: da sgrub pa pos k+ai la ya'i bsnyen pa zla
NK016(ma)001:2270: ba drug byas phyin chad nas dam tshig gi phran
NK016(ma)001:2271: tshegs las / gtor ma dus las yol ba dang /
NK016(ma)001:2272: dus che chung chags pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:2274: bsnyen bsgrub dus su mtshams ral ba dang /
NK016(ma)001:2276: lha la bsngosa pa gzhan la bsgyur ba dang /
NK016(ma)001:2277: dam bcas nas ma bskang na /
NK016(ma)001:2278: srid pa pho rgyud kyis dam can kun phrag dog che bas tha na gnyid 'thib rmug pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:2280: dbang po myos la zing zing por sems med pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:2281: rmi mtshan ngan pa la sogs pa 'ong /
NK016(ma)001:2282: de bas nyams pa che ba'i nyan yod pas /
NK016(ma)001:2283: le lo med par rgyun gdor dang /
NK016(ma)001:2284: k+ai la ya'i bsnyen dzapa la brtson par bya'o //
NK016(ma)001:2285: 'gro 'dug bza' btung gis dus su yang /
NK016(ma)001:2286: bsgom bzlas dang mchod gtor la brtson par bya /
NK016(ma)001:2287: bar mtshams su rdo rje sems dpa'i yi ge brgya pa bzlas /
NK016(ma)001:2289: gtor gang la tshig gis bshags pa bya /
NK016(ma)001:2290: nyams pa chen ce ti nag po la gos rnying pa bskon /
NK016(ma)001:2291: gtor ma dkar dmar mang du brgyan la bskang ba bya /
NK016(ma)001:2294: rta thod dar zab kyis brgyan pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:2299: de nas mnyam nyid kyis don bsgom /
NK016(ma)001:2300: dam can gyis sngags kun la k+ai la ya'i mgo non bzlas na /
NK016(ma)001:2302: rgyun gtor mi bcag pa gal che'o //
NK016(ma)001:2303: yang na k+ai la ya ngan sngags kyi bsnyen pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:2304: lha so so'i thugs kar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor du /
NK016(ma)001:2305: h'u las ngan sngags 'dus pas bskor bar bsam /
NK016(ma)001:2306: de las 'od zer dmar nag lcags kyu lta bu'i
NK016(ma)001:2307: tsh+wa tsh+wa gdab pa ltar phyogs bcur 'phros pas ras
NK016(ma)001:2309: grog spur gyi tshang bshig pa ltar 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad brlag go //
NK016(ma)001:2310: lha bsad mchod rten la sogs bshigs pa'i nang du bsgrub bya gar gnas pa ma bzod nas /
NK016(ma)001:2312: dbang po'i mngon sum du bkug nas /
NK016(ma)001:2313: bdag gis mdun du ling+ga la bstim /
NK016(ma)001:2314: de nas yang dkyil 'khor rnam pa gsum gyi thugs ka nas /
NK016(ma)001:2315: h'u dang sngags las 'od zer smug nag 'phros pa phyag gis phur pa la thim /
NK016(ma)001:2316: de la skar mada'a'am thog lta bu /
NK016(ma)001:2317: ngo bo ni sku'i sras mchog rnam pa ni drag po'i phur pa kha dog smug nag /
NK016(ma)001:2319: grangs ni tsh+wa tsh+wa ltar dpag tu med pa 'phros pas /
NK016(ma)001:2321: rkang pa'i mthil du phyung ste /
NK016(ma)001:2322: lus kyis stobs dang bral nas /
NK016(ma)001:2324: dbang po thams cad bcing nas /
NK016(ma)001:2325: nad pa tshab can lta bur gyur par bsam /
NK016(ma)001:2326: kho'i lus bsrung ba'i lha thams cad sran phung la rdo brgyab pa ltar /
NK016(ma)001:2328: lus bsrung ba'i lha dang bral bar bsam zhing yang dkar gyis thun bya'o //
NK016(ma)001:2329: yang gsung gis sras mchog gong ltar spros pas /
NK016(ma)001:2332: ngag gis stobs dang bral nas smra ba'i dbang po bcing bar bsam /
NK016(ma)001:2333: dag bsrung ba'i lha thams cad rang gis mdun du 'phen ste /
NK016(ma)001:2334: smyo zhing lkug par bsam zhing yung dmar gyis thun bya'o //
NK016(ma)001:2335: yang thugs kyi sras mchog gong ltar spros la /
NK016(ma)001:2336: kho'i snying khar phog pas srog gis khrag 'jib /
NK016(ma)001:2338: bkrag mdangs dang gzi mdangs thams cad phrog nas /
NK016(ma)001:2339: rnam shes bsrung ba'i lha ye shes sems dpa' de /
NK016(ma)001:2340: bdag h'u ka ra la a a ces bstim mo //
NK016(ma)001:2341: bdag sku gsung thugs kyis dngos grub thob ste /
NK016(ma)001:2342: kho'i lus khang stong du mar me shi ba ltar /
NK016(ma)001:2343: nag trog gis song bar bsam /
NK016(ma)001:2344: de la srung ma rnam bzhi'i sprul pa grangs med pa bdag la spros pas /
NK016(ma)001:2345: kho'i phung po bshig nas sha zos khrag 'jib /
NK016(ma)001:2346: rus pa bca' lhag mur nas /
NK016(ma)001:2347: lhag ma rdul tsam yang ma lus par bsam zhing yung nag gis thun bya'o //
NK016(ma)001:2348: de ltar yang yang du spro bsdu la sogs pa bya zhing /
NK016(ma)001:2349: dus rgyun du thun gyis brab bo //
NK016(ma)001:2350: bsdig phur nyi shu rtsa gcig dril zhing gdab bo //
NK016(ma)001:2351: de lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin yang yang dbyer zhing /
NK016(ma)001:2352: bzhi snying gcig tu dril la bsnyen pa bya'o //
NK016(ma)001:2353: de nas spu gri me 'bar gyis gdams ngag ni /
NK016(ma)001:2355: nad pa'am gzhan la byin rlabs byed pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:2356: bsrung ba byed pa dang me la phus btab pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:2357: tsha rigs sgog pa za ba dang /
NK016(ma)001:2358: bud med la spyod pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:2359: kha lud gshang lci 'dor ba dang /
NK016(ma)001:2360: de rnams spyod lam 'og nas 'byung ba dang mthun na /
NK016(ma)001:2361: sngags kyi nus pa zad par 'gyur ro //
NK016(ma)001:2362: de'i phyir na 'di la brtson par gces so //
NK016(ma)001:2364: sngags kyi nus pa me bzhin 'bar //
NK016(ma)001:2365: chos skyong rnams ni bran bzhin 'khor //
NK016(ma)001:2366: lha 'de rnams kyi bka' bzhin bsgrub //
NK016(ma)001:2368: yon tan bsam gyi mi khyab bo //
NK016(ma)001:2369: de'i phyir na spu gri me 'bar gyis gdams ngag bya ba la /
NK016(ma)001:2370: rang yi dam gzhung ltar bsgom /
NK016(ma)001:2371: ngag gis dbang po la pad+ma 'dab ma brgyad pa gcig bsgom /
NK016(ma)001:2372: de'i steng du snang ba mtha' yas sku tshon gang ba gcig bskyed /
NK016(ma)001:2373: de la 'od 'phros pas mdun gyis nam mkha' la /
NK016(ma)001:2374: bla ma dang yi dam lha tshogs dang /
NK016(ma)001:2375: chos skyong ba'i srung ma rnams kyi mthu dang nus pa thams cad bkug nas /
NK016(ma)001:2376: snang ba mtha' yas la thim /
NK016(ma)001:2377: snang ba mtha' yas yongs su gyur pa las /
NK016(ma)001:2378: yi ge h'u dmar po gcig bsam /
NK016(ma)001:2380: sngar bzhin mthu dang nus pa bkug nas h'u la bstim /
NK016(ma)001:2381: h'u de yongs su gyur pa las /
NK016(ma)001:2382: rang gis lce rdo rje rtse lnga pa gcig tu gyur par bsam /
NK016(ma)001:2383: de yang rwa dbus ma sngo ba /
NK016(ma)001:2388: de dang 'dra ba'i gre ba na /
NK016(ma)001:2390: de'i lte ba nang du ram dmar po las nyid la /
NK016(ma)001:2391: de'i steng du yi ge a dmar po me'i rang bzhin can gcig bsam /
NK016(ma)001:2393: rigs kyis yum lnga spyan drangs te /
NK016(ma)001:2394: rdo rje sems ma nam mkha'i rang bzhin can /
NK016(ma)001:2395: dbus kyis rwa sngo la thim /
NK016(ma)001:2396: na bza' dkar mo rwa dmar thim /
NK016(ma)001:2397: sangs rgyas spyan ma rwa ser la thim /
NK016(ma)001:2398: m+aa ma k+ai rwa dkar la thim /
NK016(ma)001:2399: dam tshig sgrol ma rwa ljang la thim /
NK016(ma)001:2400: rwa lnga po la de ltar so sor thim /
NK016(ma)001:2401: de la 'od kha dog sna lnga 'phros pas /
NK016(ma)001:2407: rlung gis nus mthu thams cad dang /
NK016(ma)001:2408: rgya mtsho la sogs chu'i bcud dang /
NK016(ma)001:2409: me tsha zhing bsreg pa'i nus mthu thams cad bsdus te /
NK016(ma)001:2410: ngag gis dbang po la thim /
NK016(ma)001:2411: a las byang chub rten 'brel snying pos g.yas su 'khor bar bsam /
NK016(ma)001:2412: ngag tu a nyi shu rtsa gcig brjod /
NK016(ma)001:2413: mdun gyi nam mkha' nas sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK016(ma)001:2414: yi dam lha tshogs rnams kyi ljags steng nas /
NK016(ma)001:2415: a kha ba bab pa ltar byon nas /
NK016(ma)001:2416: bdag gis lce thog gis a la thim /
NK016(ma)001:2417: ngag gis nyes skyon sdig sgrib thams cad dang /
NK016(ma)001:2418: mi dang mi ma yin gyis gnod pa thams cad bsal bar bsam /
NK016(ma)001:2419: de nas rten 'brel snying po bdun nam nyer gcig brjod /
NK016(ma)001:2420: de nas smon lam gdab pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:2421: na mo sangs rgyas kyis bka' bden pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:2422: chos kyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:2423: dge 'dun gyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:2424: dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:2425: gsang sngags thams cad kyis bka' bden pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:2426: rig sngags thams cad kyis bka' bden pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:2427: gzungs sngags thams cad kyis bka' bden pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:2428: bdag gis ngag gis dbang phyug gis mthu dang nus pa tshad med pa 'grub par gyur cig /
NK016(ma)001:2430: sangs rgyas rkang gnyis gtso ste bden pa'i mchog /
NK016(ma)001:2431: chos nyid chags pa med de bden pa'i mchog /
NK016(ma)001:2432: dge 'dun mi phyed 'dun pa gtso ste bden pa'i mchog /
NK016(ma)001:2433: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i mthus /
NK016(ma)001:2434: bdag gis ngag gis dbang phyug gis mthu dang nus pa tshad med pa 'grub par gyur cig /
NK016(ma)001:2436: chos nyid zab mo 'gyur ba med pa'i bden pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:2437: bka' rgyud bla ma rnams kyi bden pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:2438: yi dam lha tshogs rnams kyi bden pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:2439: dam pa chos skyong ba'i srung ma rnams kyi bden pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:2440: chos nyid rten 'brel 'byung ba'i mi bslu ba dang ngag gis bden pa'i mthus /
NK016(ma)001:2447: smon lam thams cad 'grub par gyur cig bya'o //
NK016(ma)001:2449: mdun gyi nam mkha' la bla ma dang /
NK016(ma)001:2451: chos skyong ba'i srung ma rnams dang /
NK016(ma)001:2452: rgyal ba'i sku la ma dad pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:2453: bla ma'i gsung bcag pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:2454: chos nyid zab mo la the tshom za ba dang /
NK016(ma)001:2456: snying po grwa chag cing zur nyams pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:2457: mchod pa lo dang zla bar 'das pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:2458: khas blang ba'i dge rtsa chag pa rnams /
NK016(ma)001:2459: bla ma dam pa rnams dang /
NK016(ma)001:2461: yi dam lha tshogs rnams dang /
NK016(ma)001:2462: chos skyong ba'i srung ma rnams kyi spyan lam du mthol lo bshags so //
NK016(ma)001:2464: de nas lha de rnams 'od du zhu nas /
NK016(ma)001:2465: rang gis ngag gis dbang po'i yi ge rnams dang /
NK016(ma)001:2466: sngags kyis nus pa rnams la thim nas /
NK016(ma)001:2467: de nas 'od kyi gang bu zhig tu zhu nas /
NK016(ma)001:2468: thugs kha'i sngags phreng dang sa bon la thim par bsam /
NK016(ma)001:2469: de nas mi dmigs pa'i ngang la dal gcig 'jog /
NK016(ma)001:2470: de ni spu gri me 'bar gyis gdams ngag ces bya'o //
NK016(ma)001:2471: de nas skabs 'dir bskul thung gyer la /
NK016(ma)001:2472: dang po thog mar bden stobs brjod /
NK016(ma)001:2473: de nas sa man dzas lha tshogs spyan drangs /
NK016(ma)001:2474: de nas rnam lnga dang sman raka gtor gsum gyi mchod /
NK016(ma)001:2478: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya ces brjod pas /
NK016(ma)001:2479: rang nyid sku mdog dmar nag dbang drag gis skur gsal nas /
NK016(ma)001:2480: 'gug byed ye shes kyis pho nya bkye ba'i dod yin pas /
NK016(ma)001:2481: skabs 'dir bden stobs brjod nas 'gug 'dren bya'o //
NK016(ma)001:2482: de nas dril thun dmigs pa ni /
NK016(ma)001:2483: rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum gyis lha dang phral ba'i las byed par bsgom /
NK016(ma)001:2484: khro bo yab yum gyis gzugs la phab pa'i las /
NK016(ma)001:2485: khra thabs yab yum gyi byad du bcug pa'i las /
NK016(ma)001:2487: bswe mo mched bzhis bsad pa'i /
NK016(ma)001:2488: re ti mched bzhis dkyil 'khor du stabs pa'i las byed par bsam la gyer ro //
NK016(ma)001:2489: de nas lhag ma bya ba la don bzhi ste /
NK016(ma)001:2491: srog gis snying po drangs zhing brten par bzhugs su gsol ba dang /
NK016(ma)001:2495: rang nyid dpal he ru ka'i ting 'dzin dang ldan pas /
NK016(ma)001:2498: mdzes pa'i phyag rgya bca' la /
NK016(ma)001:2499: de yang lhag ma'i rgyud las /
NK016(ma)001:2500: 'dzub mo bsnol byed gung mo rtse sprad pa /
NK016(ma)001:2501: mthe bong rdo rje brtan byed lag pa thal mo gdab /
NK016(ma)001:2502: +aa ra li dang pheem pheem sgra sgrogs pas /
NK016(ma)001:2503: ma tshogs mkha' 'gro 'du bar the tshom med //
NK016(ma)001:2505: gnyis pa srog gis snying po drangs zhing brtan par bzhugs su gsol ba ni /
NK016(ma)001:2506: ta ki ra tsa dza ces sogs brjod pas /
NK016(ma)001:2507: sngar nas dkyil 'khor la yod pa rnams la thim par bsgom mo //
NK016(ma)001:2509: bdag gis lce thog tu hrihdamara po gcig bsam pa la sogs gzhung bzhin no //
NK016(ma)001:2510: bzhi pa las bcol ba ni /
NK016(ma)001:2511: dam can rnams kyi bdag gis bka' nyan par bsam la /
NK016(ma)001:2513: shar gyis phyogsa nasa byung ba ni /
NK016(ma)001:2517: khrom ge sar dmag gis rgya 'bod /
NK016(ma)001:2518: srin mo'i mdur 'gros la sogs pa rnams bya'o //
NK016(ma)001:2522: gtor ma nam mkha' mthong sar bsnur la /
NK016(ma)001:2523: sman raka bran la gtor ma +aahmh'u gis 'dod yon du dmigs la /
NK016(ma)001:2526: de yang drag po'i las byed dus lhag chung tshar
NK016(ma)001:2527: nas gtor ma ma bskyang ba la dgongs gsol bya'o
NK016(ma)001:2528: // bzlog sngags 'dod la lha thams cad zhal phyir gzigs par bsam /
NK016(ma)001:2529: bzlog pa byed pa'i dus su /
NK016(ma)001:2530: gtor ma mtshon cha'i phung por bsam la chos skyong lha tshogs rnams kyi khyer nas /
NK016(ma)001:2531: byad ma'i sgrub khang steng ru brgyab pas byang ma 'khor dang bcas pa rdul du brlag par bsam /
NK016(ma)001:2532: ngan sngags sgrub pa'i dus su /
NK016(ma)001:2533: gtor ma sgrub byar bsam la /
NK016(ma)001:2534: chos skyong rnams kyi khyer nas hab thob du gsol bar bsam /
NK016(ma)001:2535: rgyun gtor bskyang dus gtor ma rin po che'i mchod sdong rtse mo gsum pa /
NK016(ma)001:2536: rtsa ba t+r+aam gis mtshan pa rtse mor 'bru gsum gyi mtshan pa la /
NK016(ma)001:2537: dang po bde bar gshegs pa thams cad la /
NK016(ma)001:2538: gnyis pas dam can srung ma /
NK016(ma)001:2539: gsum pas 'gro drug rnams la mchod sbyin gyis khyab par bsam la bskyang ngo //
NK016(ma)001:2540: de nas dz+wa la badz+ra'i sngags brjod pa tsam gyis /
NK016(ma)001:2541: rang gis gnas lnga nas mtshon cha rnams spros pas /
NK016(ma)001:2542: gzhal yas khang gis rgyab rdo rje rwa ba'i nang gis mtshon cha'i gur drug la phog /
NK016(ma)001:2543: de la mtshon cha'i tshogs spros pas /
NK016(ma)001:2544: log par 'dren par bgegs rnams bskrad /
NK016(ma)001:2545: de nas ye d+har+m+aa brjod pa tsam gyi lha tshogs rnams zhal nang du gzigs par bsam /
NK016(ma)001:2546: mtshon cha rnams tshur 'dus nas gur khang drug la thim pas /
NK016(ma)001:2547: sra zhing brtan par gyur par bsam /
NK016(ma)001:2548: de nas rting bshags bya ba ni /
NK016(ma)001:2549: rang gtso bo gnyis pa'i tshul du shar sgor gshegs par bsam la /
NK016(ma)001:2550: lus ngag yid gsum gnong 'gyong dang bcas te /
NK016(ma)001:2552: h'u badga ni ranga riga ye shesa blo dang ma ldana pasa /
NK016(ma)001:2553: ces sogs gzhung bzhin byas la /
NK016(ma)001:2554: tshar nas bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyis lha tshogs
NK016(ma)001:2555: rnams kyis cho ga lhag chad gyur pa'i nyes pa
NK016(ma)001:2556: dag pa'i gnang ba byin par bsam la /
NK016(ma)001:2557: rang gtso bo'i thugs kar thim par bsam /
NK016(ma)001:2558: de nas lha tshogs rnams kyi bkra shis pa'i dgongs
NK016(ma)001:2559: pa dang bcas pas bkra shis brjod par bsam la
NK016(ma)001:2560: / phun sum tshogas pa mang'a ba gsera gyis ri bo 'dra /
NK016(ma)001:2561: ces sogs sprin mdangs 'khrig pa'i dbyangs dang bcas pa bya'o //
NK016(ma)001:2562: de nas dkyil 'khor bsdu ba ni /
NK016(ma)001:2563: phyi snod kyis 'jig rten he ru kar brlab la /
NK016(ma)001:2565: gzhal yas khang dam can la bsdu /
NK016(ma)001:2566: dan can khro bo la bsdu /
NK016(ma)001:2567: khro bo khra thabs dang bcas pa gtso bo la bsdu /
NK016(ma)001:2568: sus mchog rnams gtso bo yab yum la bsdu /
NK016(ma)001:2570: yab thugs ka'i ye shes sems dpa' la bsdu /
NK016(ma)001:2573: h'u yang zhabs kyu la bsdu /
NK016(ma)001:2577: zla tshes thig le la bsdu /
NK016(ma)001:2578: thig le chos kyi dbyings su bstim mo //
NK016(ma)001:2579: de nas stong pa nyid la ci tsam gnas kyis bar du bzhag go //
NK016(ma)001:2580: de nas 'bru dgu brjod pa tsam gyis /
NK016(ma)001:2581: rdo rje gzhon nur wal gyis gsal bar bsgom la /
NK016(ma)001:2582: de'i spyi bor rang byung du b+h+r+aum dang kam gnyis bskyed /
NK016(ma)001:2584: lus thams cad rdo rje'i khrab zhub dang zhu lub du g.yog par bsam /
NK016(ma)001:2585: de zhu ba las rdo rje'i rgyun thag rkang ba gnyis la kha khar 'khril te /
NK016(ma)001:2590: dpral ba'i skra mtshams dang drug tu rdo rje rgya gram gyis mdud pa re re byas par bsam /
NK016(ma)001:2591: de nas 'dzub mo gnyis kyi rtse mos h'u gnyis bsgom pa'i rgyun thag de khrid pa ltar byas /
NK016(ma)001:2592: gnas drug tu rdo rje'i mdo mig bcu gnyis bsgom mo //
NK016(ma)001:2593: mdo mig g.yas na rdo rje gnod sbyin mthing nag
NK016(ma)001:2594: 'jigs la rngam pa'i sku la me 'bar bar bsgom
NK016(ma)001:2595: / g.yon na bdud rtsi thal sbyor ser nag gong ltar phyir gzigs pas srungs bar bsgom mo //
NK016(ma)001:2596: rgyun thag rtse mo phal cher smin mtshams su dar
NK016(ma)001:2597: mthing ka'i cod pan lta bur gyur par bsgom pa
NK016(ma)001:2599: rta gsad spu gsum phur pa skyi lugs kyis //
NK016(ma)001:2600: snying khrag yin pa'i nang nas mchog gyur ni //
NK016(ma)001:2601: gsang sgrub bla ma kahthoga lugs dang ni //
NK016(ma)001:2602: bkol ba dum bu'i rgyud kyi rtsa thung dang //
NK016(ma)001:2603: mngon rtogs bsnyen pa don bcu'i gzhung dang ni //
NK016(ma)001:2604: drug pa spyan drangs bdun pa dbang bskur dang //
NK016(ma)001:2605: brgyad pa sman gtor rak+ta dgu pa bstod //
NK016(ma)001:2606: de'i tshig bcad byang bu'i lhan thabs dang //
NK016(ma)001:2607: sman raka gtor ma byin gyis brlab thabs dang //
NK016(ma)001:2608: lhag ma'i cho ga rting bshags rtsa bskul dang //
NK016(ma)001:2609: bzlas pa'i man ngag tshe'i bsnyen pa dang //
NK016(ma)001:2610: sngags kyis dbye ba rtags dang mtshan bstan dang //
NK016(ma)001:2611: dngos grub blang ba'i cho ga la sogs pa //
NK016(ma)001:2612: bsdus pa'i byang bu sku bsnyen skor du 'dod //
NK016(ma)001:2613: sngags drug thun dril phur rtsa rab gnas dang //
NK016(ma)001:2614: rig 'dzin bskul pa sgrub pa'i yig chung dang //
NK016(ma)001:2615: gzer bu lha gsal dbang du bya ba dang //
NK016(ma)001:2616: phur bu rnams la sngags rnams bkod lugs dang //
NK016(ma)001:2617: brub khang bsgral ba'i da la bstan pa rnams //
NK016(ma)001:2618: gsung gi sgrub pa'i skor du 'dod par snang //
NK016(ma)001:2619: rtsa ba'i yig chung 'debs phur lha ngo sprod //
NK016(ma)001:2620: dza brdung rgyas bsdus gsal 'debs skor dang ni //
NK016(ma)001:2621: phur bu dril 'debs gdab las kyis man ngag /
NK016(ma)001:2622: 'di tsho yan chad lag len yin ces gsungs //
NK016(ma)001:2623: 'di nas sa gcod 'ong ba thugs phrin las //
NK016(ma)001:2624: lha rnams gsal zhing dbang du bsdu ba dang //
NK016(ma)001:2625: gab pa'i byang gcig gdab las dmigs pa rnams //
NK016(ma)001:2626: gdams ngag yin ces tho byang nang nas bshad //
NK016(ma)001:2627: khog dbub sngags drug rbod gtong 'gyed pa dang //
NK016(ma)001:2628: sngags drug 'khor lo bskor ba yan chad ni //
NK016(ma)001:2629: rtsa ba ngan sngags skor gyi rnam grangs yin //
NK016(ma)001:2630: bskang ba zor skor brtan gtor rab gnas dang //
NK016(ma)001:2631: ser bsrung srung 'khor ngag bsrung nad rgya dang //
NK016(ma)001:2632: gnas khang rab gnas rdol dril yung dkar sogs //
NK016(ma)001:2633: rab gnas skor rnams zhing sgrol las tshogs yin //
NK016(ma)001:2634: phur bu'i rnam grangs pad+ma'i zhal chem dang //
NK016(ma)001:2635: pad+ma'i skyes rabs rgyas 'bring gnyis po dang //
NK016(ma)001:2636: gsang sngags 'byung tshul 'bru 'grel rnams kyis ni //
NK016(ma)001:2637: rdo rje phur pa'i gsang bsgrub skor rdzogs la //
NK016(ma)001:2638: blo chen rnams kyi de la brtson par mdzod //
NK016(ma)001:2639: 'di ni blo chung don du bsnyen thabs tsam //
NK016(ma)001:2640: ban+de bdag gis bris pa'i dge ba des //
NK016(ma)001:2641: 'gro kun ku ma ra'i sa thob shog /
NK016(ma)001:2643: nam mkha' bas byas zin de kha bskang ba la /
NK016(ma)001:2644: lha'i mngon rtogs kyis skabs la /
NK016(ma)001:2645: gtso bo la grub rtags kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK016(ma)001:2646: mdzad pa rtags kyi phyag rgya la sogs zhib tu byas yod /
NK016(ma)001:2647: khro bo yab yum gyi skabs la /
NK016(ma)001:2649: nang gis dgongs pa la btags pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:2650: phyag mtshan la btags pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:2651: gdul bya la btags pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:2652: mgo bsnyen la btags pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:2653: gnyan po la btags pa dang /
NK016(ma)001:2655: yon tan la btags pa rnams zhib du byas yod /
NK016(ma)001:2656: khra thabs yab yum gyis skabs la chos mthun lo rgyus zhib du byas yod /
NK016(ma)001:2657: 'di rnams ni gsang ba mdzod kyi lde'u mig nang du bkod nas yod /
NK016(ma)001:2658: 'dir yi ge mang dog pas ma bris so //
NK016(ma)001:2659: las byang man chad lus bsrung go bgo yan chad la /
NK016(ma)001:2660: nam mkha' ba'i de la tho yig lag len bsdus pa tsam gcig bas mi snang ba la /
NK016(ma)001:2661: don bshad rgyas pa spu gri me 'bar gyis gdams ngag dang bcas pa 'di ni /
NK016(ma)001:2662: kah thog yang dgon nor bu gling zhes bya bar /
NK016(ma)001:2663: gsang sngags rdo rje 'dzin pa ye shes rgyal mtshan gyis bkod pa'o //
